{"type":"message","id":"2fbc6fe3","parentId":"f7c675bf","timestamp":"2026-04-06T00:58:40.982Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the context.md and recent memory files to understand what's going on with the different strategies.","thinkingSignature":"3228400df1ee3487636853a6ed4f34afe907319d1dc1e326ec63763c8d249afa"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jz9dmjh98tqn_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent/memory/context.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jz9dmjh98tqn_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent/memory/2026-04-04.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9690,"output":101,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31258,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775437118678,"responseId":"0622383ee1e82d65a6a733550e58e6e6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9cb1ac6c","parentId":"2fbc6fe3","timestamp":"2026-04-06T00:58:41.000Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jz9dmjh98tqn_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# memory/context.md\n\n## What this file is for\nThis file is the compact snapshot of the **current active work**. It should be fast to read and easy to refresh.\n\n## Refresh this file when\n- the primary task changes\n- the current phase changes\n- a blocker appears/disappears\n- the next step changes materially\n- the user resumes a long-running thread with “continue / go on / 继续”\n\n## Active focus\n- Add audit-grade explain/report output to the memory distill apply flow.\n- Make selective write-back observable instead of implicit.\n- Keep the main entrypoint single: `scripts/memory_distill.py`.\n\n## Current blockers\n- Free-form daily logs still contain mixed chronology, evidence, and durable lessons, so heuristic routing cannot be fully trusted without review.\n- `memory_search` is currently unavailable in this session due to provider/config failure, so memory recall validation is degraded.\n\n## Current priority artifacts\n- `scripts/memory_distill.py`\n- `reports/memory_distill_apply_review_example_report.md`\n- `reports/memory_distill_apply_review_example_result.json`\n- `memory/README.md`\n\n## Immediate next-step heuristic\n- Prefer keeping machine-readable audit data in JSON and human-readable summary in markdown.\n- Treat `apply_report` as the post-run truth source for what changed.\n- If continuing, next upgrade should target validation or shorter human summary output.\n\n## Last refreshed\n- 2026-04-02 07:16 Asia/Shanghai\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775437120997}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f98b943","parentId":"9cb1ac6c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T00:58:41.004Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jz9dmjh98tqn_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-04 日志\n\n## 今日完成的工作\n\n### MiniMax 模型接入（Day 1-5 完整记录）\n\n**Day 1**: 给 `run_tradingagents_overlay.py` 加 `--provider minimax` 选项\n- 复用 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中 `custom-proxy` provider 的完整 API key（`custom-proxy.apiKey`）\n- Endpoint: `https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1/messages`\n- 模型: `MiniMax-M2.7`，`max_tokens=32000`\n- API key 读取优先级：openclaw.json custom-proxy > secrets/model_api_keys.json minimax-portal > env MINIMAX_API_KEY\n- 容错：MiniMax 调用失败时自动降级到 mock\n\n**Day 2**: 给 `candidate_explainer` 加 MiniMax adapter\n- 新建 `ai_overlay/candidate_explainer/minimax_adapter.py`\n- 更新 `main.py` 路由：`minimax*` 前缀自动走 MiniMax adapter\n- Schema 对齐：MiniMax 的 `bull_case`/`bear_case` → `ExplainerReport.hold_case`/`risk_case`\n- 修复：`date_tag` 缺失时从 payload 注入；`validate_output` 先归一化再验证\n\n**Day 3**: 全量 18 候选 + MiniMax 真实模型\n- 成功用 `MiniMax-M2.5-HighSpeed` 处理 18 个真实候选\n- `MiniMax-M2.7` 超时，`HighSpeed` 模型更快更稳定\n- 发现 `fundamental_guard` 候选数据异常（mom20=0.0），模型正确识别并降级为 defer\n\n**Day 4**: 给 `position_explainer` 加 MiniMax adapter\n- 新建 `ai_overlay/position_explainer/minimax_adapter.py`\n- 核心问题：持仓 CSV 无实时价格 → 所有浮盈亏 N/A → 模型只能全部给 HOLD\n- 解决方案：写 `scripts/enrich_holdings_with_prices.py` 用腾讯行情 API 补全价格\n  - 腾讯 API: `https://qt.gtimg.cn/q=sz300500,sh600000,...`\n  - 响应格式：GBK 编码，分号分隔的多行数据\n  - 正则解析: `v_(\\w+)=\"([^\"]*)\"` 提取每个字段\n  - 自动计算 `unrealized_pnl_pct = (current - cost) / cost * 100`\n- 修复 CSV 列名：`symbol→ts_code`，`quantity→qty`，`cost_price` 空字符串→None\n- 修复 schema 字段映射：`bull_case`→`hold_case`，`action`→`position_advice`，`watch_triggers`→`exit_triggers`\n- 修复 `%` 后缀数字归一化\n- `position_explainer` 现在能给出有意义的 HOLD/REDUCE/EXIT 建议\n\n**Day 5**: cron 自动化\n- 写 `scripts/run_daily_overlays.sh`：编排脚本，支持手动指定日期或自动取前一交易日\n- 注册 OpenClaw cron：`openclaw cron add --name \"daily-stock-overlays\" --schedule \"0 9 20 * 1-5\" --session coding-agent --command \"./run_daily_overlays.sh\"`\n- Cron ID: `511b0e2a-cdb3-4fb7-bfad-2722afaf8455`\n- 执行时间：每周一至五 09:20（开盘前25分钟）\n- 修复 `json.loads` 控制字符问题：`strict=False`\n\n## 持仓数据（2026-04-04）\n\n23 只持仓分布于 `selected_real_positions_20260404.csv`：\n- 大部分持仓处于亏损状态（浮亏 -7% 至 -60%）\n- 1 只巨幅盈利：奥比中光(+1879%，成本 3.845 → 现价 76.12)\n- 2 只建议 EXIT：博士眼镜(-41%)、思摩尔国际(-60%)\n- 数据来源：腾讯行情 API，2026-04-03 收盘价\n\n## 文件路径速查\n\n- 项目根目录：`~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/`\n- 持仓价格脚本：`scripts/enrich_holdings_with_prices.py`\n- 编排脚本：`scripts/run_daily_overlays.sh`\n- 候选池 adapter：`ai_overlay/candidate_explainer/minimax_adapter.py`\n- 持仓 adapter：`ai_overlay/position_explainer/minimax_adapter.py`\n- Overlay 输出：`research/reports/ai_overlay/`\n- Cron 日志：`logs/daily_overlays_YYYYMMDD.log`\n\n## 已知约束\n\n- akShare 被墙，无法使用\n- 腾讯行情 API 可用，是持仓价格的主要数据源\n- 科创/港股 ticker 也可通过腾讯 API 获取\n- MiniMax API key 位置：`~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` → `models.providers.custom-proxy.apiKey`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775437121001}}
