{"type":"message","id":"0b2f8b31","parentId":"5b8dab07","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:37:46.201Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - the `is_trading_day()` in these scripts only checks weekday (Mon-Fri), not public holidays. For a proper check, it would need to check against an actual trading calendar. But checking weekday is already better than nothing - at least it's not running on weekends.\n\nHowever, the problem here is that today (April 6, Monday) is a weekday but a public holiday (Qingming Festival). The simple `weekday() < 5` check won't catch this.\n\nBut the real issue is that the cron is set to `08:40 * 1-5` - it runs on any Monday-Friday including holidays. The script `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py` doesn't have any trading day check.\n \nI need to add a proper trading day check that can handle both weekends and public holidays. The `auto_run_premarket_precheck.py` has a more sophisticated approach I should look at.","thinkingSignature":"e4c35cf33535cf8bd5384aa90102cbdb47db91f79b8e8b640a6e58888fb8f340"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5oqcbw6oixg8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -A 30 \"def is_trading_day\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35391,"output":264,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57122,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775453857385,"responseId":"062279a19dd4bb942490a97540ce502f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"986985ad","parentId":"0b2f8b31","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:37:46.229Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5oqcbw6oixg8_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def is_trading_day(date_str: str) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"\n    交易日判断：\n    1) 优先使用本地指数日历（date/trade_date）\n    2) 若本地日历过旧（目标日期晚于最后一条日历），降级为工作日判断（周一~周五）\n    \"\"\"\n    # 先准备工作日降级逻辑\n    try:\n        date_obj = datetime.strptime(date_str, \"%Y-%m-%d\")\n        weekday_fallback = date_obj.weekday() < 5\n    except Exception:\n        weekday_fallback = False\n\n    if not INDEX_CSV.exists():\n        return weekday_fallback\n\n    # 兼容两种常见列名：date / trade_date（例如 Tushare 导出的指数数据）\n    df = pd.read_csv(INDEX_CSV, usecols=lambda c: c in {\"date\", \"trade_date\"})\n    date_col = \"date\" if \"date\" in df.columns else (\"trade_date\" if \"trade_date\" in df.columns else None)\n    if date_col is None:\n        return weekday_fallback\n\n    normalized: set[str] = set()\n    for x in df[date_col].dropna().tolist():\n        s = str(x).strip()\n        if len(s) == 8 and s.isdigit():\n            normalized.add(f\"{s[:4]}-{s[4:6]}-{s[6:8]}\")\n        else:\n            normalized.add(s[:10])\n\n    if date_str in normalized:"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"def is_trading_day(date_str: str) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"\n    交易日判断：\n    1) 优先使用本地指数日历（date/trade_date）\n    2) 若本地日历过旧（目标日期晚于最后一条日历），降级为工作日判断（周一~周五）\n    \"\"\"\n    # 先准备工作日降级逻辑\n    try:\n        date_obj = datetime.strptime(date_str, \"%Y-%m-%d\")\n        weekday_fallback = date_obj.weekday() < 5\n    except Exception:\n        weekday_fallback = False\n\n    if not INDEX_CSV.exists():\n        return weekday_fallback\n\n    # 兼容两种常见列名：date / trade_date（例如 Tushare 导出的指数数据）\n    df = pd.read_csv(INDEX_CSV, usecols=lambda c: c in {\"date\", \"trade_date\"})\n    date_col = \"date\" if \"date\" in df.columns else (\"trade_date\" if \"trade_date\" in df.columns else None)\n    if date_col is None:\n        return weekday_fallback\n\n    normalized: set[str] = set()\n    for x in df[date_col].dropna().tolist():\n        s = str(x).strip()\n        if len(s) == 8 and s.isdigit():\n            normalized.add(f\"{s[:4]}-{s[4:6]}-{s[6:8]}\")\n        else:\n            normalized.add(s[:10])\n\n    if date_str in normalized:","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775453866225}}
