{"type":"message","id":"6af1d863","parentId":"46325570","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:37:51.244Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qnumo1skcwfn_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport subprocess\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nSCRIPTS_DIR = ROOT / \"scripts\"\nBUILD_SCRIPT = SCRIPTS_DIR / \"build_daily_quant_analysis_json.py\"\nRENDER_MD_SCRIPT = SCRIPTS_DIR / \"render_daily_quant_analysis_md.py\"\nRENDER_FEISHU_SCRIPT = SCRIPTS_DIR / \"render_daily_quant_analysis_feishu.py\"\nDELIVERY_STATUS_SCRIPT = SCRIPTS_DIR / \"manage_daily_quant_analysis_delivery.py\"\n\n\ndef run_step(command: list[str]) -> None:\n    subprocess.run(command, check=True)\n\n\ndef main() -> int:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"Daily investment research brief orchestrator\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"mode\", nargs=\"?\", default=\"morning\", choices=[\"morning\", \"close\"], help=\"Report mode\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--date-tag\", default=\"\", help=\"Optional trade date tag override\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--json-only\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"Only build structured JSON artifact\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--skip-feishu-render\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"Skip generating Feishu summary text artifact\")\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--skip-delivery-status-sync\",\n        action=\"store_true\",\n        help=\"Skip updating delivery status bookkeeping artifacts\",\n    )\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    build_cmd = [sys.executable, str(BUILD_SCRIPT)]\n    if args.date_tag:\n        build_cmd.extend([\"--date-tag\", args.date_tag])\n    run_step(build_cmd)\n\n    if not args.json_only:\n        run_step([sys.executable, str(RENDER_MD_SCRIPT)])\n        if not args.skip_feishu_render:\n            run_step([sys.executable, str(RENDER_FEISHU_SCRIPT)])\n            if not args.skip_delivery_status_sync:\n                run_step([sys.executable, str(DELIVERY_STATUS_SCRIPT), \"--action\", \"sync\"])\n\n    report_kind = \"收盘版\" if args.mode == \"close\" else \"盘前/盘中版\"\n    suffix = \"，已同步 delivery 状态账本（dry-run bookkeeping）\" if (not args.json_only and not args.skip_feishu_render and not args.skip_delivery_status_sync) else \"\"\n    print(f\"[日报主线已完成] {report_kind}，已按结构化 JSON -> Markdown/Feishu 摘要流程生成{suffix}\")\n    return 0\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    raise SystemExit(main())"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport subprocess\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nSCRIPTS_DIR = ROOT / \"scripts\"\nBUILD_SCRIPT = SCRIPTS_DIR / \"build_daily_quant_analysis_json.py\"\nRENDER_MD_SCRIPT = SCRIPTS_DIR / \"render_daily_quant_analysis_md.py\"\nRENDER_FEISHU_SCRIPT = SCRIPTS_DIR / \"render_daily_quant_analysis_feishu.py\"\nDELIVERY_STATUS_SCRIPT = SCRIPTS_DIR / \"manage_daily_quant_analysis_delivery.py\"\n\n\ndef run_step(command: list[str]) -> None:\n    subprocess.run(command, check=True)\n\n\ndef main() -> int:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"Daily investment research brief orchestrator\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"mode\", nargs=\"?\", default=\"morning\", choices=[\"morning\", \"close\"], help=\"Report mode\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--date-tag\", default=\"\", help=\"Optional trade date tag override\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--json-only\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"Only build structured JSON artifact\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--skip-feishu-render\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"Skip generating Feishu summary text artifact\")\n    parser.add_argument(\n        \"--skip-delivery-status-sync\",\n        action=\"store_true\",\n        help=\"Skip updating delivery status bookkeeping artifacts\",\n    )\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    build_cmd = [sys.executable, str(BUILD_SCRIPT)]\n    if args.date_tag:\n        build_cmd.extend([\"--date-tag\", args.date_tag])\n    run_step(build_cmd)\n\n    if not args.json_only:\n        run_step([sys.executable, str(RENDER_MD_SCRIPT)])\n        if not args.skip_feishu_render:\n            run_step([sys.executable, str(RENDER_FEISHU_SCRIPT)])\n            if not args.skip_delivery_status_sync:\n                run_step([sys.executable, str(DELIVERY_STATUS_SCRIPT), \"--action\", \"sync\"])\n\n    report_kind = \"收盘版\" if args.mode == \"close\" else \"盘前/盘中版\"\n    suffix = \"，已同步 delivery 状态账本（dry-run bookkeeping）\" if (not args.json_only and not args.skip_feishu_render and not args.skip_delivery_status_sync) else \"\"\n    print(f\"[日报主线已完成] {report_kind}，已按结构化 JSON -> Markdown/Feishu 摘要流程生成{suffix}\")\n    return 0\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    raise SystemExit(main())","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775453871240}}
{"type":"message","id":"812c130d","parentId":"6af1d863","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:38:00.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the structure. The `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py` doesn't have a trading day check. I need to add one.\n\nLooking at the `auto_run_premarket_precheck.py` approach, it uses an index CSV to check trading days and falls back to weekday. I should add a similar check to `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py`.\n\nThe simplest fix is to add a trading day check at the start of `main()`. I need to decide:\n1. Should I import the existing `is_trading_day` from `auto_run_premarket_precheck.py` or replicate it?\n2. What should the behavior be on non-trading days - skip entirely or just output a minimal notice?\n\n\nI'll go with adding a check that skips the report generation on non-trading days since the briefing is specific to trading activity. Let me write the fix.","thinkingSignature":"a75df8faf55c93ce9a03bd3d595c93bff6b6876f02824ee95bdc23f408a6aeab"},{"type":"text","text":"\n问题确认了。`run_daily_investment_research_brief.py` 完全没有交易日判断，只靠 cron 的 `1-5` 触发——但 `1-5` 把清明节这种假日也包含进来了。\n\n我来给它加一个交易日门禁，非交易日直接跳过并打印原因：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zg6my8kqjqh6_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":25,"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":36729,"output":312,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58508,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775453871245,"responseId":"062279afe1fae326579379b2b137b805"}}
