{"type":"message","id":"878ada4a","parentId":"5b41abe7","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:38:55.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the issue clearly now:\n1. The `investment_research_brief_morning.log` shows the script ran today (2026-04-06) at 08:30 and produced output for `20260402` (the last trading day), even though today is a holiday.\n2. The script `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py` didn't check if today is a trading day - it just ran and produced output with the stale `20260402` data.\n3. Now with my fix, it should skip on non-trading days.\n\nBut wait - the log shows the output is from `20260402` (April 2). \n\nThe script ran today but used stale data from the last trading day instead of recognizing that today is a holiday and shouldn't produce any output at all. My fix handles this by adding the trading day check. I should also verify whether the cron job for the pre-open briefing (`investment-research-background-preopen-0840`) is separate from the `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py` script or if they're connected.\n\nLooking at the schedule format, the `08:40来福投研会-盘前值班` cron uses `40 8 * * 1-5` which fires every Monday-Friday at 08:40. Since the briefing came from the same morning script at 08:30, I need to check if these are actually the same cron or if the preopen briefing is a different scheduled task that also needs the holiday check applied.","thinkingSignature":"24db18ab52dfdb737699d132f6f4810e2a890622f743bcb0f23e89fb54904764"},{"type":"text","text":"今天 08:30 的日志证实了——脚本跑在清明节假期、输出了 `20260402` 的旧数据，没有检测到假日。\n\n**刚才已修复：** 在 `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py` 入口加了交易日判断：\n\n```\n非 A 股交易日（2026-04-06 周一），跳过日报生成。\n```\n\n- 优先查指数日历 CSV（`daily_zz2000_closes.csv`）\n- 找不到日历时降级为工作日判断（周一~五）\n- 加 `--force` 参数可手动override，用于调试\n\n**另外还有一个问题**：盘前值班 cron `08:40 来福投研会-盘前值班` 今天 08:40 也触发了。我看看它是不是走的另一条链路：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fmlc9fi19u8c_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system -name \"cron_daily_investment_research_brief.sh\" 2>/dev/null; cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/cron_daily_investment_research_brief.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41785,"output":580,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63832,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775453921866,"responseId":"062279e2378a95ff1eae290ce7c7ec8e"}}
