{"type":"message","id":"a563df46","parentId":"3345b983","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:41:51.496Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Tencent API shows the latest data is from 20260403 (April 3), and today's date (April 6) doesn't have any data - confirming today is not a trading day.\n\nNow I have a way to check: use the Tencent API and check if the date field matches today. If not, it's either a weekend or a holiday.\n\nLet me now update the trading day check in `run_investment_research_background_cycle.py` to use this approach. I'll replace the simple weekend check with a more robust one.","thinkingSignature":"33d55b2d910081593850c130a263a6bcfd6f9f2dce6fbcd7e6b98292d9966f7d"},{"type":"text","text":"腾讯行情 API 证实：最新数据日期是 `20260403`，今天 `20260406` 无数据——确认是非交易日。\n\n我把这个检查加到 `run_investment_research_background_cycle.py`，替换掉刚才那个只检查周末的版本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tv4zxkkwf1vu_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_investment_research_background_cycle.py","old_string":"    now = datetime.now()\n    today_str = now.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n\n    # 非交易日静默跳过（只检查工作日，盘中/盘后阶段不输出任何内容）\n    if now.weekday() >= 5:\n        print(f\"[{now:%Y-%m-%d %H:%M}] 非 A 股交易日（周末），值班周期 {args.cycle} 跳过。\", flush=True)\n        return\n\n    REPORT_DIR.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)","new_string":"    now = datetime.now()\n    today_str = now.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n\n    # -------- 交易日判断（腾讯行情 API + 周末兜底）--------\n    is_trading_day = False\n    if now.weekday() < 5:  # 先排除周末\n        try:\n            import urllib.request\n            req = urllib.request.Request(\n                \"https://qt.gtimg.cn/q=sh000001\",\n                headers={\"User-Agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0\"},\n            )\n            with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=5) as resp:\n                content = resp.read().decode(\"gbk\", errors=\"replace\")\n            for line in content.split(\";\"):\n                if \"sh000001\" in line:\n                    parts = line.split(\"~\")\n                    if len(parts) > 30:\n                        date_str = parts[30].strip()[:8]  # e.g. \"20260403\"\n                        market_date = f\"{date_str[:4]}-{date_str[4:6]}-{date_str[6:8]}\"\n                        is_trading_day = market_date == today_str\n                    break\n        except Exception:\n            is_trading_day = False  # 网络异常时保守跳过\n\n    if not is_trading_day:\n        weekday_name = [\"周一\", \"周二\", \"周三\", \"周四\", \"周五\", \"周六\", \"周日\"][now.weekday()]\n        print(f\"[{now:%Y-%m-%d %H:%M}] 非 A 股交易日（{weekday_name}），值班周期 {args.cycle} 跳过。\", flush=True)\n        return\n    # -----------------------------------------------------\n\n    REPORT_DIR.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":60298,"output":690,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82455,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775454098907,"responseId":"06227a93e2eeb6c84f4f85fc7fb2dd18"}}
