{"type":"message","id":"94e1244f","parentId":"cc57f325","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:42:10.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me also verify the other fix I made to `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py` has the same issue - it only checks weekdays, not public holidays. Let me update it similarly.Actually, looking at the `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py` fix I made earlier, I used the index CSV to check trading days. But the index CSV doesn't exist, so it falls back to weekday check. Let me update it to use the same Tencent API approach.Let me also update `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py` to use the same Tencent API approach.","thinkingSignature":"3edde3af276a47317be5091e8f667ff989a7c0422496b042b1ca6ebedd50c3b6"},{"type":"text","text":"同样更新 `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py`，把指数 CSV 判断升级为腾讯 API 判断：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wkzyzaentuvf_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_daily_investment_research_brief.py","old_string":"# 找指数日频 CSV 用于交易日判断\nINDEX_CSV = REPORT_DIR / \"daily_zz2000_closes.csv\"\n\n\ndef _is_trading_day(date_str: str) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"判断是否为 A 股交易日。优先用指数日历，降级为工作日（周一~五）。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        date_obj = datetime.strptime(date_str, \"%Y-%m-%d\")\n        weekday_fallback = date_obj.weekday() < 5\n    except Exception:\n        weekday_fallback = False\n\n    if not INDEX_CSV.exists():\n        return weekday_fallback\n\n    try:\n        df = pd.read_csv(INDEX_CSV, usecols=lambda c: c in {\"date\", \"trade_date\"})\n        date_col = \"date\" if \"date\" in df.columns else (\"trade_date\" if \"trade_date\" in df.columns else None)\n        if date_col is None:\n            return weekday_fallback\n\n        normalized: set[str] = set()\n        for x in df[date_col].dropna().tolist():\n            s = str(x).strip()\n            if len(s) == 8 and s.isdigit():\n                normalized.add(f\"{s[:4]}-{s[4:6]}-{s[6:8]}\")\n            else:\n                normalized.add(s[:10])\n\n        return date_str in normalized\n    except Exception:\n        return weekday_fallback","new_string":"# 找指数日频 CSV 用于交易日判断（已废弃，改用腾讯行情 API）\nINDEX_CSV = REPORT_DIR / \"daily_zz2000_closes.csv\"\n\n\ndef _is_trading_day(date_str: str) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"判断是否为 A 股交易日。优先用腾讯行情 API，降级为工作日（周一~五）。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        date_obj = datetime.strptime(date_str, \"%Y-%m-%d\")\n        weekday_fallback = date_obj.weekday() < 5\n    except Exception:\n        weekday_fallback = False\n\n    if date_obj.weekday() >= 5:  # 周末直接跳过\n        return False\n\n    try:\n        import urllib.request\n        req = urllib.request.Request(\n            \"https://qt.gtimg.cn/q=sh000001\",\n            headers={\"User-Agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0\"},\n        )\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=5) as resp:\n            content = resp.read().decode(\"gbk\", errors=\"replace\")\n        for line in content.split(\";\"):\n            if \"sh000001\" in line:\n                parts = line.split(\"~\")\n                if len(parts) > 30:\n                    mkt_str = parts[30].strip()[:8]\n                    market_date = f\"{mkt_str[:4]}-{mkt_str[4:6]}-{mkt_str[6:8]}\"\n                    return market_date == date_str\n                break\n        return weekday_fallback\n    except Exception:\n        return weekday_fallback"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61207,"output":851,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83525,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775454116545,"responseId":"06227aa40716f4a650a5a0b840789a12"}}
