{"type":"message","id":"61c0e0e4","parentId":"5d5f9c0d","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:44:09.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, only my 3 changed files are staged. Let me commit them.","thinkingSignature":"14bea34ff50a1f3361c09c0ff95a85e91f28d14446d51b9b6e7e605fef054084"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_33v21ulkm1gy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace && git commit -m \"fix: 非交易日（节假日）跳过盘前值班与日报生成\n\n- run_investment_research_background_cycle.py:\n  新增腾讯行情API交易日判断（sh000001日期字段），周末/节假日直接返回，跳过整个值班流程\n  附赠--force参数用于手动调试\n\n- run_daily_investment_research_brief.py:\n  同上，替换失效的指数CSV方案，改为腾讯API判断\n  移除pandas依赖\n\n- auto_run_premarket_precheck.py:\n  同上，替换失效的指数CSV方案\n  移除pandas和INDEX_CSV依赖\n  腾讯API返回的30号字段即为市场交易日期（yyyymmddHHMMSS）\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69312,"output":206,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90985,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775454242822,"responseId":"06227b238cc380db4d6cf436b98b5da7"}}
