{"type":"message","id":"607636fd","parentId":"c7fa9a17","timestamp":"2026-04-06T05:44:22.023Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the commit was successful. Now let me also update the memory/context.md with this fix information.Actually, let me just give a summary to the user of what was fixed and why.","thinkingSignature":"47a533a84bdc63cffebbfea31924051d0973455c7af9757f81f52b9904dd959a"},{"type":"text","text":"完成。总结一下今天的问题和修复：\n\n**问题根因：** cron 的 `1-5` 只排除周末，不排除 A 股节假日（清明节、春节、国庆等）。今天清明节假期，三个脚本都在跑。\n\n**已修复（3 个文件）：**\n\n| 文件 | 修复内容 |\n|------|---------|\n| `run_investment_research_background_cycle.py` | 加了腾讯行情 API 交易日判断，API 返回的 `sh000001` 日期字段 vs 今天，非交易日直接 return |\n| `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py` | 同上逻辑，同时移除已失效的 pandas/CSV 依赖 |\n| `auto_run_premarket_precheck.py` | 同上，去掉 INDEX_CSV 逻辑，改为腾讯 API |\n\n**判断逻辑：**\n```\nif 周末 → 非交易日\nif 腾讯API返回的最近交易日期 == 今天 → 交易日\nelse → 非交易日（节假日）\n```\n\n**腾讯 API 验证：** `sh000001`（上证指数）最新数据日期是 `20260403`，今天 `20260406` 无数据 → 确认非交易日 ✅\n\n下次清明节等假期不会再触发这些值班机制了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":65650,"output":291,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87408,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775454249220,"responseId":"06227b296d84700bb258470f531d58d8"}}
