{"type":"message","id":"0b11aa98","parentId":"b67faee0","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:30:34.573Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The paper trading system uses merged signals from `signals/merged/merged_signals_{date_tag}.csv`. These signals come from the signal generation pipeline. The v4.3 strategy would generate signals through the Qlib pipeline.\n\nSo to add a v4.3 paper trading profile, I need to:\n1. Create a new `paper_trading_v4_3_v1.json` config\n2. Create a corresponding `paper_live_trading_v4_3_v1.json` config\n3. Make sure the v4.3 strategy generates signals to a dedicated path\n\n\n4. Update the paper trading script to include this new profile\n\nBut the core problem is that the paper trading system pulls signals from the merged signals pipeline, and the v4.3 strategy needs to feed into that. The most practical solution is to create a new profile config for v4.3 that references the Qlib strategy parameters, then ensure the signal generation pipeline outputs v4.3 signals to the appropriate path so the paper trading system can consume them. I'm realizing the core issue: the v4.3 strategy with its new breadth and turnover parameters isn't currently generating signals to the merged signals file that paper trading reads from. Rather than modifying the complex signal generation pipeline right now, the simpler approach is to set up a dedicated paper trading profile for v4.3 that mirrors the live trading config, initialize it with the new strategy parameters, and ensure the signal generation routes v4.3 output to the paper trading system's expected location.\n\nI'll create the necessary config files for the v4.3 paper profile and check how the shell script handles multiple profiles to make sure they're all included in the run.","thinkingSignature":"2f91330e2fcf572b92ecae54e96cf51c4169c3060719c84a338ffa14cd38f851"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aoh7r3n1tu66_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92790,"output":403,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114660,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775457023196,"responseId":"062285ffa0b2879f357762082b27a368"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf73df1d","parentId":"0b11aa98","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:30:34.601Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_aoh7r3n1tu66_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\n\nROOT=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")/..\" && pwd)\"\nWORKSPACE_ROOT=\"$(cd \"$ROOT/../..\" && pwd)\"\nPYRUN=\"$ROOT/scripts/cron_python.sh\"\nDATE_TAG=\"${1:-$(date +%Y%m%d)}\"\nTICKETS_FILE=\"${2:-}\"\nRUN_MODE=\"${3:-${PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_MODE:-eod}}\"\nRUN_HEAVY_REPORTS=\"${PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS:-}\"\n\ncd \"$ROOT\"\n\nexport LITELLM_LOCAL_MODEL_COST_MAP=true\nexport PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_MODE=\"$RUN_MODE\"\n\"$PYRUN\" --runtime-only\n\nif [[ -z \"$RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS\" ]]; then\n  if [[ \"$RUN_MODE\" == \"morning_open\" ]]; then\n    RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS=\"0\"\n  else\n    RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS=\"1\"\n  fi\nfi\n\n\"$PYRUN\" scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py --date \"$DATE_TAG\"\n\nrun_profile() {\n  local config_file=\"$1\"\n  local orders_file\n  local prep_cmd=(\"$PYRUN\" scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py --config \"$config_file\" --date \"$DATE_TAG\")\n  if [[ -n \"$TICKETS_FILE\" ]]; then\n    prep_cmd+=(--tickets \"$TICKETS_FILE\")\n  fi\n\n  \"${prep_cmd[@]}\"\n\n  orders_file=\"$(\"$PYRUN\" --no-runtime-log - \"$config_file\" \"$DATE_TAG\" <<'PY'\nimport json\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nproject_root = Path.cwd()\nsys.path.insert(0, str(project_root / \"scripts\"))\nfrom paper_profile_utils import profile_slug_from_config, report_path\n\ncfg = json.loads(Path(sys.argv[1]).read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\ndate_tag = sys.argv[2]\nslug = profile_slug_from_config(cfg)\nprint(report_path(project_root / \"research\" / \"reports\", \"orders\", profile_slug=slug, date_tag=date_tag))\nPY\n)\"\n\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/run_paper_trading_sim_v1.py --trading-mode paper --config \"$config_file\" --date \"$DATE_TAG\" --orders \"$orders_file\"\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_paper_trading_dashboard.py --config \"$config_file\"\n}\n\nrun_profile \"config/paper_trading_defensive_v1.json\"\nrun_profile \"config/paper_trading_balanced_v1.json\"\nrun_profile \"config/paper_trading_aggressive_v1.json\"\n\nfor PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG in \\\n  \"$ROOT/config/strategy_probe_guard_defensive_v1.json\" \\\n  \"$ROOT/config/strategy_probe_guard_balanced_v1.json\" \\\n  \"$ROOT/config/strategy_probe_guard_aggressive_v1.json\"\ndo\n  if [[ -f \"$PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG\" ]]; then\n    if ! \"$PYRUN\" scripts/run_strategy_probe_guard.py --config \"$PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG\" --date \"$DATE_TAG\" --push; then\n      echo \"[ERROR] probe guard failed config=${PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG} date=${DATE_TAG}\" >&2\n      exit 1\n    fi\n    if ! \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_strategy_probe_daily_reconciliation.py --config \"$PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG\" --date \"$DATE_TAG\"; then\n      echo \"[ERROR] daily reconciliation failed config=${PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG} date=${DATE_TAG}\" >&2\n      exit 1\n    fi\n  fi\ndone\n\n\"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_paper_trading_comparison_dashboard.py \\\n  --configs \\\n    config/paper_trading_defensive_v1.json \\\n    config/paper_trading_balanced_v1.json \\\n    config/paper_trading_aggressive_v1.json\n\nif [[ \"$RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS\" == \"1\" ]]; then\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_today_stock_strategy_report.py --date \"$DATE_TAG\"\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_strategy_performance_panel.py\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_control_tower_daily.py\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_cto_real_data_dashboard.py\nfi\n\nif [[ \"$RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS\" == \"1\" && \"$RUN_MODE\" == \"eod\" && -f \"$WORKSPACE_ROOT/scripts/run_investment_research_event_watch.py\" ]]; then\n  \"$PYRUN\" \"$WORKSPACE_ROOT/scripts/run_investment_research_event_watch.py\"\nfi"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\n\nROOT=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")/..\" && pwd)\"\nWORKSPACE_ROOT=\"$(cd \"$ROOT/../..\" && pwd)\"\nPYRUN=\"$ROOT/scripts/cron_python.sh\"\nDATE_TAG=\"${1:-$(date +%Y%m%d)}\"\nTICKETS_FILE=\"${2:-}\"\nRUN_MODE=\"${3:-${PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_MODE:-eod}}\"\nRUN_HEAVY_REPORTS=\"${PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS:-}\"\n\ncd \"$ROOT\"\n\nexport LITELLM_LOCAL_MODEL_COST_MAP=true\nexport PAPER_PROFILE_RUN_MODE=\"$RUN_MODE\"\n\"$PYRUN\" --runtime-only\n\nif [[ -z \"$RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS\" ]]; then\n  if [[ \"$RUN_MODE\" == \"morning_open\" ]]; then\n    RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS=\"0\"\n  else\n    RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS=\"1\"\n  fi\nfi\n\n\"$PYRUN\" scripts/run_intraday_risk_recheck.py --date \"$DATE_TAG\"\n\nrun_profile() {\n  local config_file=\"$1\"\n  local orders_file\n  local prep_cmd=(\"$PYRUN\" scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py --config \"$config_file\" --date \"$DATE_TAG\")\n  if [[ -n \"$TICKETS_FILE\" ]]; then\n    prep_cmd+=(--tickets \"$TICKETS_FILE\")\n  fi\n\n  \"${prep_cmd[@]}\"\n\n  orders_file=\"$(\"$PYRUN\" --no-runtime-log - \"$config_file\" \"$DATE_TAG\" <<'PY'\nimport json\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nproject_root = Path.cwd()\nsys.path.insert(0, str(project_root / \"scripts\"))\nfrom paper_profile_utils import profile_slug_from_config, report_path\n\ncfg = json.loads(Path(sys.argv[1]).read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\ndate_tag = sys.argv[2]\nslug = profile_slug_from_config(cfg)\nprint(report_path(project_root / \"research\" / \"reports\", \"orders\", profile_slug=slug, date_tag=date_tag))\nPY\n)\"\n\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/run_paper_trading_sim_v1.py --trading-mode paper --config \"$config_file\" --date \"$DATE_TAG\" --orders \"$orders_file\"\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_paper_trading_dashboard.py --config \"$config_file\"\n}\n\nrun_profile \"config/paper_trading_defensive_v1.json\"\nrun_profile \"config/paper_trading_balanced_v1.json\"\nrun_profile \"config/paper_trading_aggressive_v1.json\"\n\nfor PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG in \\\n  \"$ROOT/config/strategy_probe_guard_defensive_v1.json\" \\\n  \"$ROOT/config/strategy_probe_guard_balanced_v1.json\" \\\n  \"$ROOT/config/strategy_probe_guard_aggressive_v1.json\"\ndo\n  if [[ -f \"$PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG\" ]]; then\n    if ! \"$PYRUN\" scripts/run_strategy_probe_guard.py --config \"$PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG\" --date \"$DATE_TAG\" --push; then\n      echo \"[ERROR] probe guard failed config=${PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG} date=${DATE_TAG}\" >&2\n      exit 1\n    fi\n    if ! \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_strategy_probe_daily_reconciliation.py --config \"$PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG\" --date \"$DATE_TAG\"; then\n      echo \"[ERROR] daily reconciliation failed config=${PROBE_GUARD_CONFIG} date=${DATE_TAG}\" >&2\n      exit 1\n    fi\n  fi\ndone\n\n\"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_paper_trading_comparison_dashboard.py \\\n  --configs \\\n    config/paper_trading_defensive_v1.json \\\n    config/paper_trading_balanced_v1.json \\\n    config/paper_trading_aggressive_v1.json\n\nif [[ \"$RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS\" == \"1\" ]]; then\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_today_stock_strategy_report.py --date \"$DATE_TAG\"\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_strategy_performance_panel.py\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_control_tower_daily.py\n  \"$PYRUN\" scripts/generate_cto_real_data_dashboard.py\nfi\n\nif [[ \"$RUN_HEAVY_REPORTS\" == \"1\" && \"$RUN_MODE\" == \"eod\" && -f \"$WORKSPACE_ROOT/scripts/run_investment_research_event_watch.py\" ]]; then\n  \"$PYRUN\" \"$WORKSPACE_ROOT/scripts/run_investment_research_event_watch.py\"\nfi","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775457034595}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c525519","parentId":"bf73df1d","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:30:48.259Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture. To add a v4.3 paper trading profile, I need to:\n\n1. Create `paper_trading_v4_3_v1.json` (the top-level profile config)\n2. Create `paper_live_trading_v4_3_v1.json` (the live trading execution config with v4.3 params)\n3. Update `run_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh` to add the new profile in three places:\n   - `run_profile` call\n   - probe guard config list\n   - comparison dashboard `--configs`\n\nThe v4.3 strategy uses Qlib breadth strategy params. \n\nFor the paper trading setup, I'll base it on the existing aggressive profile structure but swap in the v4.3 Qlib strategy params, setting initial cash to 1,000,000 and starting from 20260407 (the next trading day after the holiday).\n\nNow I'm creating the necessary files: the paper trading configuration, the corresponding live trading parameters for v4.3, and updating the shell script to register this new profile in the system.","thinkingSignature":"3c1fe45835375a04ec89cdf46f034b09f232954bd6bc1e82f1c576e5e2e44615"},{"type":"text","text":"现在清楚了，模拟盘系统是通过 `run_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh` 驱动、需要创建两个配置文件并注册进去。\n\n两步并行走：\n\n**第一步：创建 paper profile 配置**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xn70kaf327p0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/paper_trading_v4_3_v1.json << 'EOF'\n{\n  \"strategy_id\": \"paper_trading_v4_3_v1\",\n  \"profile_slug\": \"v4_3_aggressive\",\n  \"profile_name\": \"小市值筹码v4.3进取型\",\n  \"initial_cash\": 1000000.0,\n  \"start_date_tag\": \"20260407\",\n  \"live_config\": \"config/paper_live_trading_v4_3_v1.json\",\n  \"execution_config\": \"config/paper_live_trading_v4_3_v1.json\",\n  \"history_dir\": \"data/processed/a_stock_history\",\n  \"benchmark\": {\n    \"name\": \"中证2000\",\n    \"symbol\": \"00