{"type":"message","id":"6aff1386","parentId":"46fa0422","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:38:47.520Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`run_close_review_v2.py` also doesn't have a trading day check. But wait - should the close review run on non-trading days? If the market is closed, there's nothing to review for that trading day. However, if it's the end of a holiday weekend (like now), and the script checks \"yesterday\" or \"today\" which is a non-trading day, it might try to review the last trading day.Actually, looking at the cron schedule again, the close review cron runs at 16:30 on weekdays. If it's a holiday, the cron won't fire because it's `1-5` only (Mon-Fri). But wait - today is Monday April 6, which is weekday 0 (Monday). \n\nSo the cron `30 16 * * 1-5` WOULD fire on a Monday holiday. I need to add a trading day check to `run_close_review_v2.py` as well. Let me look at the main function to understand how it handles dates.","thinkingSignature":"14a2dc7754279108553005cdce9cae0621952e465b58b3e2bac83ddc51ada178"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dqkr8uudznnp_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":789,"limit":30,"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_close_review_v2.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":96605,"output":280,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118352,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775457517718,"responseId":"062287ed97b89c2762a428ba15869082"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c576f28e","parentId":"6aff1386","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:38:47.536Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dqkr8uudznnp_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"收盘复盘生成 v2（新增个股分析）\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--date\", default=\"\", help=\"YYYYMMDD，默认今天\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--orders\", default=\"\", help=\"可选：指定 live_orders csv\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--journal\", default=\"\", help=\"可选：指定 live_journal csv\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--skip-stock-analysis\", action=\"store_true\",\n                        help=\"跳过个股分析（analyzer_service 调用）\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    date_tag = args.date.strip() if args.date.strip() else datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n\n    config = load_json(CONFIG_PATH)\n    live_json, live_payload = load_dated_live_system_payload(date_tag, report_dir=REPORT_DIR)\n\n    orders = resolve_orders_file(date_tag, args.orders)\n    journal = Path(args.journal).resolve() if args.journal else REPORT_DIR / f\"live_journal_v1_{date_tag}.csv\"\n\n    files = {\n        \"orders\": str(orders),\n        \"journal\": str(journal),\n        \"premarket\": str(REPORT_DIR / f\"live_premarket_risk_v1_{date_tag}.md\"),\n    }\n\n    orders_stats = summarize_orders(orders)\n    queue_resolution = close_pending_user_confirm_queue(orders, date_tag)\n    journal_stats = summarize_journal(journal)\n\n    # ── Layer 3: 个股分析 ───────────────────────────────────────────\n    stock_analyses = None\n    if not args.skip_stock_analysis:\n\n[60 more lines in file. Use offset=819 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775457527529}}
{"type":"message","id":"a430f927","parentId":"c576f28e","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:39:03.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to add the same check to `run_close_review_v2.py`. Let me do that.","thinkingSignature":"f74aef6e3f1923668bee2843f49ab647c45a37aff31db575fe4a51635c03f0bb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v2oxlxaewjny_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_close_review_v2.py","old_string":"def main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"收盘复盘生成 v2（新增个股分析）\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--date\", default=\"\", help=\"YYYYMMDD，默认今天\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--orders\", default=\"\", help=\"可选：指定 live_orders csv\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--journal\", default=\"\", help=\"可选：指定 live_journal csv\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--skip-stock-analysis\", action=\"store_true\",\n                        help=\"跳过个股分析（analyzer_service 调用）\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    date_tag = args.date.strip() if args.date.strip() else datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n\n    config = load_json(CONFIG_PATH)","new_string":"def _is_trading_day(date_str: str) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"判断指定日期是否为 A 股交易日（腾讯行情 API + 工作日降级）。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        date_obj = datetime.strptime(date_str, \"%Y%m%d\")\n        if date_obj.weekday() >= 5:\n            return False\n    except Exception:\n        return False\n    try:\n        import urllib.request\n        req = urllib.request.Request(\n            \"https://qt.gtimg.cn/q=sh000001\",\n            headers={\"User-Agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0\"},\n        )\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=5) as resp:\n            content = resp.read().decode(\"gbk\", errors=\"replace\")\n        for line in content.split(\";\"):\n            if \"sh000001\" in line:\n                parts = line.split(\"~\")\n                if len(parts) > 30:\n                    mkt_str = parts[30].strip()[:8]\n                    market_date = f\"{mkt_str[:4]}-{mkt_str[4:6]}-{mkt_str[6:8]}\"\n                    date_formatted = f\"{date_str[:4]}-{date_str[4:6]}-{date_str[6:8]}\"\n                    return market_date == date_formatted\n                break\n        return date_obj.weekday() < 5\n    except Exception:\n        return date_obj.weekday() < 5\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"收盘复盘生成 v2（新增个股分析）\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--date\", default=\"\", help=\"YYYYMMDD，默认今天\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--orders\", default=\"\", help=\"可选：指定 live_orders csv\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--journal\", default=\"\", help=\"可选：指定 live_journal csv\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--skip-stock-analysis\", action=\"store_true\",\n                        help=\"跳过个股分析（analyzer_service 调用）\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    date_tag = args.date.strip() if args.date.strip() else datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n\n    if not _is_trading_day(date_tag):\n        weekday = [\"周一\", \"周二\", \"周三\", \"周四\", \"周五\", \"周六\", \"周日\"][datetime.strptime(date_tag, \"%Y%m%d\").weekday()]\n        date_formatted = f\"{date_tag[:4]}-{date_tag[4:6]}-{date_tag[6:8]}\"\n        print(f\"[{datetime.now():%Y-%m-%d %H:%M}] 非 A 股交易日（{date_formatted} {weekday}），跳过盘后复检。\", flush=True)\n        return\n\n    config = load_json(CONFIG_PATH)"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":95086,"output":822,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117375,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775457527538,"responseId":"062287f7896b26ca9afafbbdf14d5c25"}}
