{"type":"message","id":"c4f4df56","parentId":"fb1b759e","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:39:36.346Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me answer the question about the panel update. Zhang Ling mentioned that we should also update the panel and remove stopped/deleted paper trading panels from it.\n\nLet me summarize what we've done so far and confirm what still needs to be done about the panel.\n\nThe panel update involves `panel_profile_registry.py` and potentially `generate_strategy_performance_panel.py`. Zhang Ling said we should:\n1. Remove stopped/deleted panels from the panel\n2. Add v4_3_aggressive to the panel\n\nI asked for confirmation earlier but Zhang Ling didn't explicitly answer - she was replying to the data source health check message. Let me address both questions clearly.","thinkingSignature":"e2c9b6af522b45f77e7b8853caaccc7380509e3b24cf45b5ea40b91345e23921"},{"type":"text","text":"已提交。现在总结今天所有修复：\n\n**本次清明节触发排查，共修复了 6 个脚本的交易日判断：**\n\n| 脚本 | 触发时机 | 状态 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| `run_daily_investment_research_brief.py` | 08:30 盘前日报 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| `run_investment_research_background_cycle.py` | 08:40/10:30/16:30 值班 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| `run_investment_research_data_source_health_probe.py` | 09:35 数据源巡检 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| `run_intraday_risk_recheck.py` | 盘中风险复检 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| `run_close_review_v2.py` | 16:30 盘后复检 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| `auto_run_premarket_precheck.py` | 09:20 盘前强检 | ✅ 已修复 |\n\n---\n\n关于**量化面板更新**（删除已停止纸盘 + 加入 v4_3_aggressive）——我还没动，需要你确认一下理解是否正确：\n\n**现在面板有 6 个纸盘，你希望：**\n- **exit_dual**（年化 -96.5%）→ ❌ 删除\n- **exit_tight**（年化 -96.55%）→ ❌ 删除  \n- **alpha55**（数据停在 3/30，5天没更新）→ ❌ 删除\n- **defensive / balanced / aggressive**（旧系统，年化 -13%~-9%）→ ❌ 移出（被 v4.3 取代）\n- **v4_3_aggressive**（OOS 年化 58.48%）→ ✅ 加入\n\n这样面板**只剩 v4_3_aggressive 一个**。确认吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":96602,"output":526,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118595,"cost":{"input":0,"