{"type":"message","id":"44c29430","parentId":"c4f4df56","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:39:39.262Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5201064cc0b0c4d86b2c52d49ed\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-06 14:36 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5201064cc0b0c4d86b2c52d49ed]\n张玲: 我一直不懂什么是纸盘"}],"timestamp":1775457579257}}
{"type":"message","id":"a69d1971","parentId":"44c29430","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:39:58.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zhang Ling is asking what \"paper trading\" (纸盘/paper profiles) means. This is a genuine conceptual question. Let me explain it clearly.\n\nPaper trading = simulated trading with fake money, using real market data and real strategy signals, but no real orders are placed.\n\nKey differences:\n- **Live trading (实盘)**: Real money, real orders through broker API\n- **Paper trading (纸盘/模拟盘)**: Fake money, strategy runs with same logic/signals, generates simulated fills and P&L, but no real trades\n\nThe name \"paper\" comes from \"paper trading\" - trading on paper instead of with real money.","thinkingSignature":"33f59ce6bd90a45892e019065989f7d5cfdf8f04f6d919362276db8a1f407534"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好问题。用大白话说：\n\n**纸盘 = 用假钱跑真实策略**\n\n你的策略逻辑照常跑，该买就买该卖就卖，但下的不是真单——而是\"如果真的买了，按真实行情算下来盈亏是多少\"。\n\n举例：\n\n| | 实盘 | 纸盘 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 钱 | 真钱，亏了真的少钱 | 虚拟100万，亏了只是数字变少 |\n| 下单 | 券商API，真成交 | 不下单，只记录\"如果成交会怎样\" |\n| 行情 | 实时价格 | 同样的真实价格 |\n| 目的 | 赚钱 | **验证策略在真实行情下是否靠谱** |\n\n---\n\n**为什么需要纸盘？**\n\n策略回测（用历史数据算）是\"马后炮\"，纸盘是\"实战模拟\"：\n\n- 回测说年化 58% → 纸盘真行情跑几个月看是不是真有 58%\n- 策略在熊市会不会爆仓 → 纸盘跑一段时间才能发现\n- 参数在最新行情下是否还适用 → 纸盘比回测更真实\n\n你的 v4.3 新策略就是，先用纸盘跑一段时间（比如1个月），数据漂亮了、没问题了，再切实盘。这叫 **paper-to-live**（从模拟到真实）。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":416,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":98657,"totalTokens":120614,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775457579260,"responseId":"0622882b0dcd3d4bf8c5a05e759f8e48"}}
{"type":"message","id":"535d087a","parentId":"a69d1971","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:41:35.438Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5201171324a4c4584f56584db2b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-06 14:41 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5201171324a4c4584f56584db2b]\n张玲: 不着急删除失败的纸盘吧，毕竟今年三月的行情不好"}],"timestamp":1775457695434}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba12ca7c","parentId":"535d087a","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:41:45.485Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zhang Ling is saying not to rush to delete the failed paper trading profiles, because March 2026 had bad market conditions. She's right - those strategies might not actually be bad, just caught in a bad market. We should keep them for now and revisit later.\n\nSo the plan is:\n- Don't delete the failed paper profiles yet\n- Just add v4_3_aggressive to the panel\n- Maybe revisit panel cleanup later\n\nLet me just acknowledge and confirm the current plan.","thinkingSignature":"32c72187c9de62f2060f6f5862410258358340386069fb47fea737f2bb71c067"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 有道理，今年三月整体行情差，确实不能单看那段时间的收益就下结论。保留观察是对的。\n\n那今天关于面板的操作就先只做一件事：\n\n**加入 v4_3_aggressive**（新增小市值筹码v4.3进取型纸盘）\n\n其他纸盘暂时不动，过段时间行情好了再复盘哪些该留。继续保留观察。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":183,"cacheRead":120702,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120885,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775457695436,"responseId":"062288a158629fcb3824982f7488b8bf"}}
