{"type":"message","id":"c2a0c6e2","parentId":"2417b476","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:51:30.102Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file looks fine - the ROOT assignment ends with `pwd)\"` - there's no missing quote. It seems like the issue was my edit old_string had the wrong content. The file's first few lines look correct. Let me just try to write the whole new file with the trading day check at the beginning.\n\nActually wait, let me look at the current file content more carefully. The issue was that my oldText for the edit had:\n```\nROOT=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")/..\" && pwd)\ncd \"$ROOT\"\n```\n\nBut the actual file has:\n```\nROOT=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")/..\" && pwd)\"\n\n\ncd \"$ROOT\"\n```\n\nSo the actual file has them on SEPARATE lines. My oldText had them on the SAME line. That was the mismatch. Let me just write the whole file.","thinkingSignature":"74e379e8105440e73567da5b040b757031655bb02bc740ffd5ccfb4058bd3fc5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qktr21v340sa_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PYEOF'\n# Read the current file and add trading day check after the cd line\nfilepath = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_breadth_strict_oos_paper_daily.sh'\ncontent = open(filepath).read()\n\ncheck = '''# 非交易日跳过\nMKT_OK=$(python3 -c \"\nimport urllib.request, datetime\ntry:\n    req = urllib.request.Request('https://qt.gtimg.cn/q=sh000001', headers={'User-Agent':'Mozilla/5.0'})\n    with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=5) as r:\n        c = r.read().decode('gbk', errors='replace')\n    for line in c.split(';'):\n        parts = line.split('~')\n        if len(parts) > 30:\n            mkt = parts[30].strip()[:8]\n            today = datetime.datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n            print('yes' if mkt == today else 'no')\n            break\n    else:\n        print('no')\nexcept:\n    print('yes')\n\" 2>/dev/null)\nif [[ \"$MKT_OK\" != \"yes\" ]]; then\n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] 非 A 股交易日，跳过 breadth_strict_oos_paper\"\n    exit 0\nfi\n'''\n\n# Insert after \"cd $ROOT\"\nnew_content = content.replace('cd \"$ROOT\"\\n', 'cd \"$ROOT\"\\n' + check + '\\n', 1)\nopen(filepath, 'w').write(new_content)\nprint('Done, check added after cd $ROOT')\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98151,"output":554,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120172,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775458275724,"responseId":"06228ae38642f9834e8365057ff74100"}}
