{"type":"message","id":"0b98aa28","parentId":"e06b800c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:52:51.008Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So `run_tester_scheduled_guard.py` calls `run_investment_research_event_watch.py`. Since I already added a trading day check to `run_investment_research_event_watch.py`, the guard would be protected through that call. \n\nBut I should check the main() to see if there's other output before the call to event_watch.","thinkingSignature":"2dc1b416868f8073f3625525dc8edbcc6b405bdcd6f6dbf6960cb322bb1912b1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1ki1hq0ydkbv_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":63,"limit":40,"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_tester_scheduled_guard.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":100169,"output":138,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121774,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775458365419,"responseId":"06228b3d8bbcadcf871159063dee6cfd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d4b0f52","parentId":"0b98aa28","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:52:51.028Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1ki1hq0ydkbv_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def main() -> None:\n    date_tag = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n    runtime = load_json(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / 'runtime_risk_state_latest.json')\n    # P1-001 follow-up：优先使用 generated_at 更新的那份报告，避免盘中更新 latest 但 dated 仍为旧数据\n    dated_report = load_json(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / f'today_stock_strategy_report_{date_tag}.json')\n    latest_report = load_json(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / 'today_stock_strategy_report_latest.json')\n    report = latest_report\n    if dated_report and latest_report:\n        dated_ts = parse_dt(dated_report.get('generated_at'))\n        latest_ts = parse_dt(latest_report.get('generated_at'))\n        if dated_ts > latest_ts:\n            report = dated_report\n    elif dated_report:\n        report = dated_report\n    event_watch = load_json(REPORT_DIR / f'investment_research_event_watch_{date_tag}.json')\n    event_watch = maybe_refresh_event_watch(runtime, event_watch, date_tag)\n\n    issues: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n\n    latest_runtime = runtime.get('latest_runtime') or {}\n    report_trade_date = str(report.get('trade_date') or '').replace('-', '')\n    runtime_date = str(runtime.get('date_tag') or '')\n    report_mode = str(report.get('risk_mode') or '')\n    runtime_mode = str(latest_runtime.get('mode') or '')\n\n    if runtime and report:\n        if runtime_date == date_tag and report_trade_date == date_tag:\n            if runtime_mode and report_mode and runtime_mode != report_mode:\n                append_issue(issues, 'critical', 'runtime_report_mode_mismatch', f'runtime={runtime_mode}, report={report_mode}')\n            if latest_runtime.get('halt_new_buy') != report.get('halt_new_buy'):\n                append_issue(issues, 'critical', 'runtime_report_halt_mismatch', f\"runtime={latest_runtime.get('halt_new_buy')} report={report.get('halt_new_buy')}\")\n            if latest_runtime.get('market_breadth') != report.get('market_breadth'):\n                append_issue(issues, 'high', 'runtime_report_breadth_mismatch', f\"runtime={latest_runtime.get('market_breadth')} report={report.get('market_breadth')}\")\n\n    # halt 状态下模拟盘不应仍保留当日新增买入\n    if report_trade_date == date_tag and bool(report.get('halt_new_buy')):\n        for profile in ['defensive','balanced','aggressive']:\n            acc = load_json(QUANT_REPORT_DIR / f'paper_{profile}_account_v1_{date_tag}.json')\n            if acc:\n                buys = int(acc.get('today_buy_count') or 0)\n\n[125 more lines in file. Use offset=103 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775458371020}}
{"type":"message","id":"0729eeae","parentId":"5d4b0f52","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:53:15.286Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `run_tester_scheduled_guard.py` script does things unrelated to the trading day - it's checking runtime consistency, reading reports, etc. It's not a \"generate output on non-trading days\" type of script per se. It's more of an internal consistency check.\n\nLooking at the cron list earlier:\n```\ntester_guard 35 * * * * 1-5\n```\n\nThis runs every 35 minutes during trading hours (1-5), and the script is an internal consistency checker. Since it's `1-5` in the cron, it's not specific about holidays. But the script's behavior on holidays would be to read yesterday's or stale data and compare it.\n \nI'm realizing the core issue is that the cron expression `35 * * * * 1-5` doesn't account for Chinese holidays like the Qingming Festival, so the script fires even on non-trading days. Since the event watch and data source health probe already have trading day guards in place, those should prevent unnecessary executions. Looking at what `run_tester_scheduled_guard.py` actually does, it just reads state files and checks consistency rather than generating trading signals, so it wouldn't produce the kind of noisy output that the event watch would. it won't generate a Feishu message. Looking at the cron schedule and what the user said earlier, they specifically flagged the 临时会商 (event watch) and 数据源巡检 (data source health) as issues. The `run_tester_scheduled_guard` runs every 35 minutes and just produces a local report file without sending messages. The guard script itself runs on a trading day check, so it should be protected now. I think the main issue has been addressed with the event watch guard, and the tester scheduled guard might produce empty reports on holidays but that's just local file output. I think I've covered the key issues the user flagged—临时会商 and 数据源巡检 are now protected by trading day checks, so I'll hold off on the tester guard unless they specifically ask.","thinkingSignature":"91743ac775047eae7c2a591d165f5979e2a2354388efffa4e7bcf6070366cb20"},{"type":"text","text":"\n`run_tester_scheduled_guard.py` 是内部一致性检查（读本地文件、无 Feishu 推送），影响较小，不改它了。\n\n今天的非交易日修复已经覆盖了所有会产生噪音输出的核心 cron：\n\n| 脚本 | 今天触发原因 |\n|------|------------|\n| 临时会商 09:45 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 数据源健康巡检 09:35 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 盘前值班 08:40 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 盘前日报 08:30 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 盘前强检 09:20 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 宽度纸盘 09:15（aggressive + strict OOS） | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 纸盘 profiles 09:35 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 盘中风险复检 11:00/13:30/14:20 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 保守影子盘 16:10 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 盘中值班 10:30 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 盘后复检 16:30 | ✅ 已修复 |\n\n清明节后第一个交易日（4月7日）起，所有值班 cron 恢复自动触发。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":96681,"output":665,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118813,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775458371030,"responseId":"06228b43845189a15b7ca1b8a1aa2248"}}
