{"type":"message","id":"d41da224","parentId":"c0c4e2c1","timestamp":"2026-04-06T10:47:30.058Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o7mxzwng7swu_1","toolName":"tavily_extract","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n  \"count\": 1,\n  \"tookMs\": 2799,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_fetch\",\n    \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/discovery/item/69d2477a000000002003bd72?app_platform=android&ignoreEngage=true&app_version=9.24.0&share_from_user_hidden=true&xsec_source=app_share&type=normal&xsec_token=CB6YZl4bPxqYRzn2zs7nZNqU7-TJbptQI7dZmRPURwfGg%3D&author_share=1&shareRedId=N0g1Rjk5PUs6TEZFSkozRzo0Pzw9OT0_&apptime=1775472402&share_id=7c5ba7e1e2204922a1b6c197cd30f09e&share_channel=copy_link&appuid=5b3f649b4eacab3a41659476&xhsshare=CopyLink\",\n      \"rawContent\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"240d32ef676484ef\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Fetch\\n---\\n![](http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061847/68a5aed16c039ddf7fd5d21e11b82189/spectrum/1040g34o31uj1ebgc1m105o99jrn09d1nepvqr20!h5_1080jpg)\\n![](http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061847/1af171ee099dfb3f0989b37ba0b7fc77/spectrum/1040g34o31uj1ec7djg105o99jrn09d1nbncu4ko!h5_1080jpg)\\n![](http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061847/29ed2d0802f53890e15e34bd5732ab28/spectrum/1040g34o31uj1ecutis005o99jrn09d1nmep12h0!h5_1080jpg)\\n![](http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061847/211bccfd80cc3f1af3f8a50cf6e9b178/1040g2sg31uj48o9mige05o99jrn09d1nobaq32o!h5_1080jpg)\\n![](http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061847/3f767fba5bf368df494a48a57da09f6c/1040g2sg31uj48o9migeg5o99jrn09d1nru14tjg!h5_1080jpg)\\n![](http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061847/ac846a22a103a0918201c31589a0dda2/spectrum/1040g0k031uj1edmd34005o99jrn09d1n95kiseg!h5_1080jpg)\\n![](http://sns-webpic-qc.xhscdn.com/202604061847/a59ece136cfc1cf7edb9b053c535caa0/spectrum/1