](https://github.com/users/karpathy/packages?repo_name=autoresearch). [Please reload this page](https://github.com/karpathy/autoresearch). ## [Contributors](https://github.com/karpathy/autoresearch/graphs/contributors). [Please reload this page](https://github.com/karpathy/autoresearch). *   [Python 83.4%](https://github.com/karpathy/autoresearch/search?l=python). *   [Jupyter Notebook 16.6%](https://github.com/karpathy/autoresearch/search?l=jupyter-notebook). *   [Contact](https://support.github.com/?tags=dotcom-footer).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f439ccbf62cd13cd\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.8974172\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"190e0d1337de5719\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhat is Karpathy's Autoresearch and how does it work?\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"190e0d1337de5719\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://softmaxdata.com/blog/autoresearch/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"79847fbb9b622284\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGitHub - karpathy/autoresearch: AI agents running research on single-GPU nanochat training automatically. AI agents running research on single-GPU nanochat training automatically - karpathy/autoresearch. The agent modifies the training code, runs a 5-minute experiment, checks whether the result improved, keeps or discards the change, and repeats — indefinitely. The agent reads program.md, understands that it should loop forever, run experiments, track results, and make keep/discard decisions — and then it just does it. OpenClaw (formerly known as Clawdbot/Moltbot) is an open-source AI agent that runs on your local machine and connects through messaging apps like Telegram to automate real-world tasks — research, email triage, file management, web browsing, deployment, and more. Similarly, the interesting thing about autoresearch isn't that models get trained — it's that an AI agent is making research decisions about what to try next, learning from failures, and iterating autonomously with no human in the loop.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"79847fbb9b622284\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.8863518\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7279eb5101b1f5ff\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGitHub - karpathy/autoresearch: AI agents automatically conducting ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7279eb5101b1f5ff\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://ht-x.com/posts/2026/03/github-karpathy-autoresearch-ai-agents-running-res/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e1c13de370973159\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n[↓Skip to main content](https://ht-x.com/posts/2026/03/github-karpathy-autoresearch-ai-agents-running-res/#main-content). 3.   [GitHub - karpathy/autoresearch: AI agents automatically conducting research on single-GPU nanochat training](https://ht-x.com/posts/2026/03/github-karpathy-autoresearch-ai-agents-running-res/)/. Its comprehensive features and cross-platform compatibility make it a valuable asset for optimizing database performance, ensuring data security, and enhancing overall productivity.](https://ht-x.com/posts/2026/01/introduction-mcp-toolbox-for-databases/). ![Image 2: autoresearch repository preview](https://ht-x.com/images/posts/2026/03/autoresearch-ai-agents-running-research-on-single-gpu-nanochat-training-automatically-2.webp). ## Summary [#](https://ht-x.com/posts/2026/03/github-karpathy-autoresearch-ai-agents-running-res/#summary). ## Introduction [#](https://ht-x.com/posts/2026/03/github-karpathy-autoresearch-ai-agents-running-res/#introduction). ## What It Does [#](https://ht-x.com/posts/2026/03/github-karpathy-autoresearch-ai-agents-running-res/#what-it-does). ## Why It’s Amazing [#](https://ht-x.com/posts/2026/03/github-karpathy-autoresearch-ai-agents-running-res/#why-its-amazing). ### Dynamic and Contextual: [#](https://ht-x.com/posts/2026/03/github-karpathy-autoresearch-ai-agents-runni