{"type":"message","id":"c8d65b51","parentId":"63a75640","timestamp":"2026-04-06T10:49:09.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. The Xiaohongshu note is about Karpathy's **autoresearch** project on GitHub. Let me summarize this for the user.\n\nKey facts:\n1. **Project name**: `karpathy/autoresearch` on GitHub\n2. **What it does**: AI agents that autonomously run research experiments on LLM training\n3. **Core idea**: Give an AI Agent a small but real LLM training environment, and let it modify code, run 5-minute experiments, check results, and iterate autonomously\n4. **Code size**: ~630 lines of Python\n\n\n5. **Infrastructure**: Single GPU capable, built on nanochat as the training core with three essential files (prepare.py, train.py, program.md), and already accumulating significant community interest with 66.5k stars on GitHub\n6. **Real-world results**: The system ran 276 experiments autonomously over two days and identified 29 improvements that enhanced validation loss\n7. **Key insight**: Karpathy is reimagining research workflows through distributed AI agents across countless branches rather than relying on a single master branch approach\n8. **Interesting connection**: OpenClaw (formerly Clawdbot) actually gets a direct mention in the GitHub README as a concrete example of an open-source AI agent in action","thinkingSignature":"7981017d73477f5470034ad411c77aa7b6672871267e6d0560a5c0d2ddb4fab2"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 找到了，是 **Karpathy 的 `autoresearch`** 项目，不是知识库——是他在 GitHub 上新开源的一个 AI Agent 自动化科研框架。\n\n---\n\n**一句话总结**：给 AI 一个真实可跑的小型 LLM 训练环境，AI 自己改代码、跑实验、看结果、决定是保留还是丢弃，然后循环——全自动、24小时不停、零人类干预。\n\n**项目信息：**\n- **GitHub**: [github.com/karpathy/autoresearch](https://github.com/karpathy/autoresearch)\n- **Stars**: 66.5k（现在应该更多）\n- **代码量**: 仅 630 行 Python\n- **依赖**: 单张 GPU、Python 3.10+、uv 包管理工具\n\n**核心三个文件：**\n- `prepare.py` — 数据准备、工具函数\n- `train.py` — Agent 唯一会修改的训练主程序\n- `program.md` — 人类用自然语言写的研究目标，Agent 照着执行\n\n**实验结果**（Karpathy 自己跑出来的）：\n- 跑了 **276 次实验**，筛出 **29 项有效改进**\n- 48 小时内把 nanochat 模型的训练效率提升了约 **11%**\n- GPT-2 达标所需时间从 2.02 小时缩短到 1.8 小时\n\n**最震撼的点**：Karpathy 认为当前的 GitHub 设计（所有分支最终必须合并回 master）不适合 AI 高频探索。他想做的是：**让成千上万个 AI Agent 在无数分支里异步协作，不再受单一 master 分支的限制**——就像 SETI@home 那种分布式科研模式。\n\n**README 里还专门提到了 OpenClaw（Clawdbot）**——说它是一个\"开源 AI Agent，跑在本地机器上，通过 Telegram 等消息应用连接，完成研究、邮件分类、文件管理、网页浏览、部署等任务\"。算是点名认可了。\n\n---\n\n你研究这个是想做什么？感觉跟量化投研系统的自动化研究流程很相关——也许可以用来自动探索策略参数？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97370,"output":699,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119536,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775472526404,"responseId":"0622c28e40d491da5b46efbe0d085327"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e58365eb","parentId":"c8d65b51","timestamp":"2026-04-06T10:51:23.577Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b520d4c6d90a0c4237766c5d62a0\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-06 18:51 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b520d4c6d90a0c4237766c5d62a0]\n张玲: 让我的openclaw和ai变得更聪明，帮我挣钱"}],"timestamp":1775472683572}}
{"type":"message","id":"226e4fc8","parentId":"e58365eb","timestamp":"2026-04-06T10:51:52.039Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to use autoresearch or similar techniques to make their OpenClaw and AI smarter at making money (investing). Let me think about what this means in context:\n\n1. Karpathy's autoresearch is about letting AI agents autonomously run experiments on LLM training\n2. The user has a quantitative investment research system\n3. They want to apply this to their OpenClaw + investment system\n\nThis is a big and interesting idea. Let me think about what could actually be done:\n\n**For the OpenClaw agent itself (general intelligence):**\n- The agent could use autoresearch-like loop to improve its own workflows\n- Memory distillation, skill improvement, self-debugging\n\n**For the investment system:**\n- Auto-paramter tuning: instead of manual walk-forward analysis, let an AI agent continuously explore parameter space\n- Strategy discovery: let an AI agent generate and test new alpha signals\n\n\n- Regime detection and adaptation where the AI identifies market regimes and adjusts strategy accordingly\n\nI should be honest about what's realistically achievable here. Autoresearch works well for LLM training because the feedback loop is tight and experiments are fast, but investment strategies have a fundamental problem—the signal-to-noise ratio is extremely low, market regimes shift, and backtesting overfitting is a real danger. That said, there are some concrete applications worth exploring, like automated hyperparameter tuning for their existing strategies.\n\nThe most promising immediate use cases would be using an AI coding agent to continuously audit their codebase for bugs and improvements, running their walk-forward analysis pipeline more frequently, and potentially adapting autoresearch concepts for synthetic data generation or strategy stress testing. I should give them a practical roadmap rather than overselling the approach.","thinkingSignature":"fe454ecd85b669d5a89b1e0a838a4cf970579e5d074230e7e6bf9e72a00fa4ba"},{"type":"text","text":"\n[[reply_to_current]] 这个方向很有意思，但要分清楚两件事——\n\n**你的目标：AI 帮你挣钱 = 两个维度**\n\n---\n\n**维度1：让 OpenClaw 更聪明（Agent 能力）**\n\n这个用 autoresearch 思路是可行的，但不需要改 OpenClaw 本身。真正有用的是：\n\n- **让子 Agent 自动探索更好的工作流**：比如让 Codex/Claude Code 定期审计你的投研系统代码，找可以优化的点\n- **自动生成报告、分析**：你现在每天大量 cron 输出的是结构化文本，可以让 AI 在非活跃时段主动反思、总结、提出改进建议\n- **Skill 自动进化**：你系统里有大量 skill，可以让 AI 定期检查哪些 skill 过时了、哪些可以合并、哪些缺失\n\n这个我现在就能做，不需要额外安装。\n\n---\n\n**维度2：让策略更聪明（赚钱）**\n\n这个是更值得探索的方向，但 autoresearch 的直接套用有**根本性问题**：\n\n| autoresearch 擅长的 | 量化策略的难点 |\n|---|---|\n| 5分钟一次反馈循环 | A股市场信号太稀疏，一轮可能要几天 |\n| 实验结果客观（loss下降） | 策略好坏要看夏普，但你无法区分是策略强还是运气好 |\n| 同一任务反复训练 | 市场在变化，历史规律不一定在未来有效 |\n\n**真正适合 AI 在投研上做的事**：\n\n1. **参数自动巡检**：你的 walk-forward 现在是手工跑的，可以让 AI 定期（比如每周）自动跑参数搜索，发现比当前基准更好的参数就告警\n2. **策略思路生成**：让 AI 读你现在的所有策略代码、论文、研报，生成新的因子/规则假设\n3. **代码自动优化**：审计现有系统代码，找出逻辑漏洞、可以简化的路径\n\n---\n\n**我的建议**：先做第 1 项（参数自动巡检），因为：\n- 你刚确认了 v4.3 策略参数（Walk-Forward OOS 58.48%）\n- 可以让 AI 每周自动跑一次 walk-forward，监控参数是否开始漂移\n- 挣钱的策略发现 + 持续监控，这个链条是完整的\n\n要做吗？我来设计一下这个 cron 的逻辑。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":799,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":99197,"totalTokens":121537,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775472683576,"responseId":"0622c32c922902c5639a3d30c23c1739"}}
