{"type":"message","id":"d54b6a91","parentId":"fbe434d0","timestamp":"2026-04-06T10:56:45.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The windows CSV has the per-window data. Let me update the auto-audit script to read from the windows CSV rather than trying to get it from the summary JSON. Let me update the script.","thinkingSignature":"63d496dda315d454d2f980f28db789ec3f79fac316711b2a05bbe0051fc9ed25"},{"type":"text","text":"\n发现问题了——窗口级指标存在 `*_windows.csv` 里，不在 summary JSON 里。修复脚本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rseuqq0aobgu_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_strategy_param_auto_audit.py","old_string":"def find_latest_summary() -> Path | None:\n    \"\"\"找到最新的 aggressive walk-forward summary JSON。\"\"\"\n    summaries = sorted(\n        REPORT_DIR.glob(\"aggressive_walkforward_summary_*.json\"),\n        key=lambda p: p.stat().st_mtime,\n        reverse=True,\n    )\n    for s in summaries:\n        # 跳过临时/调试文件\n        if \"_audit\" in s.name or \"_temp\" in s.name:\n            continue\n        return s\n    return None\n\n\ndef load_latest_summary(path: Path) -> dict | None:\n    try:\n        return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n\n\ndef extract_latest_window(d: dict) -> dict | None:\n    \"\"\"从 summary 中提取最晚的一个 test window。\"\"\"\n    windows = d.get(\"windows\", [])\n    if not windows:\n        return None\n    # 按 test_end 排序，取最晚的\n    latest = max(windows, key=lambda w: w.get(\"test_end\", \"\"))\n    return latest","new_string":"def find_latest_summary() -> tuple[Path | None, Path | None]:\n    \"\"\"找到最新的 aggressive walk-forward summary + windows 文件。\"\"\"\n    summaries = sorted(\n        REPORT_DIR.glob(\"aggressive_walkforward_summary_*.json\"),\n        key=lambda p: p.stat().st_mtime,\n        reverse=True,\n    )\n    summary_path = None\n    for s in summaries:\n        if \"_audit\" in s.name or \"_temp\" in s.name or \"_report\" in s.name:\n            continue\n        summary_path = s\n        break\n\n    if summary_path is None:\n        return None, None\n\n    # 找对应的 windows CSV（同名替换）\n    windows_path = REPORT_DIR / summary_path.name.replace(\"summary\", \"windows\")\n    if not windows_path.exists():\n        windows_path = None\n        # 尝试找最新的 windows 文件\n        windows_list = sorted(\n            REPORT_DIR.glob(\"aggressive_walkforward_windows_*.csv\"),\n            key=lambda p: p.stat().st_mtime,\n            reverse=True,\n        )\n        for w in windows_list:\n            if w.stat().st_mtime <= summary_path.stat().st_mtime:\n                windows_path = w\n                break\n\n    return summary_path, windows_path\n\n\ndef load_latest_summary(path: Path) -> dict | None:\n    try:\n        return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n\n\ndef extract_latest_window(summary: dict, windows_csv: Path | None) -> dict | None:\n    \"\"\"从 windows CSV 提取最晚的一个 test window（比 summary JSON 更准确）。\"\"\"\n    if windows_csv and windows_csv.exists():\n        try:\n            import pandas as pd\n            df = pd.read_csv(windows_csv)\n            if \"test_end\" in df.columns and \"test_sharpe_daily\" in df.columns:\n                df = df.sort_values(\"test_end\")\n                row = df.iloc[-1]\n                return row.to_dict()\n        except Exception:\n            pass\n    # 降级：从 summary 中取\n    windows = summary.get(\"windows\", [])\n    if not windows:\n        return None\n    return max(windows, key=lambda w: w.get(\"test_end\", \"\"))"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":103821,"output":822,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126110,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775472987161,"responseId":"0622c45b9aa5542916ee581caa718a9d"}}
