{"type":"message","id":"1fa6afb9","parentId":"65d91517","timestamp":"2026-04-06T10:58:20.260Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pzbry0yf5g6a_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.28 (f9b1079) — If it works, it's automation; if it breaks, it's a \"learning opportunity.\"\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":853,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.28 (f9b1079) — If it works, it's automation; if it breaks, it's a \"learning opportunity.\"\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775473100257}}
