{"type":"message","id":"8f802d74","parentId":"0d67739c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:09:59.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's no webhook configured. I need to set up a Feishu webhook. A Feishu webhook requires:\n1. A Feishu group (or just a bot in a group)\n2. A webhook URL from Feishu\n\nTo get a webhook in Feishu:\n1. Open the Feishu group\n2. Group Settings → Bots → Add Bot → \"Custom Bot\" (自定义机器人)\n3. Get the webhook URL (looks like `https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v2/hook/xxx`)\n\n\nI should guide the user through setting this up and retrieving the webhook URL, since I'll need it to complete the script configuration.","thinkingSignature":"7f2be89f1ff6e81f2c443c84cbb1c716e59782745b2998c3075dda8b25363fa6"},{"type":"text","text":"目前没有配置飞书 webhook。需要先在飞书群里创建一个自定义机器人来获取 webhook URL。\n\n**步骤（2分钟）：**\n\n1. 打开飞书群（来福投研会那个群）\n2. 点右上角 **群设置** → **机器人** → **添加机器人**\n3. 选 **\"自定义机器人\"**\n4. 名字随便取，比如「参数巡检机器人」\n5. 点**添加**，复制生成的 **Webhook URL**\n\n把 URL 发给我，我来：\n1. 保存到配置文件\n2. 更新脚本让告警自动推送到飞书群\n\n（Webhook URL 形如：`https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v2/hook/xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx`）"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108334,"output":302,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130103,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775473789695,"responseId":"0622c77d67e8de1c6079069610ee6816"}}
