{"type":"message","id":"e76d25f2","parentId":"a00cb169","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:31:51.269Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_es58wcs7k4og_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.28 (f9b1079) — I'm not AI-powered, I'm AI-possessed. Big difference.\n\nUsage: openclaw message [options] [command]\n\nSend, read, and manage messages and channel actions\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help   Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  ban          Ban a member\n  broadcast    Broadcast a message to multiple targets\n  channel      Channel actions\n  delete       Delete a message\n  edit         Edit a message\n  emoji        Emoji actions\n  event        Event actions\n  kick         Kick a member\n  member       Member actions"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2003,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.28 (f9b1079) — I'm not AI-powered, I'm AI-possessed. Big difference.\n\nUsage: openclaw message [options] [command]\n\nSend, read, and manage messages and channel actions\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help   Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  ban          Ban a member\n  broadcast    Broadcast a message to multiple targets\n  channel      Channel actions\n  delete       Delete a message\n  edit         Edit a message\n  emoji        Emoji actions\n  event        Event actions\n  kick         Kick a member\n  member       Member actions","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775475111267}}
