{"type":"message","id":"fb0a7d9c","parentId":"c1a710bd","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:31:59.232Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_t1v9jfc0xfv4_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.28 (f9b1079) — Gateway online—please keep hands, feet, and appendages inside the shell at all times.\n\nUsage: openclaw message send [options]\n\nSend a message\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id (accountId)\n  --buttons <json>       Telegram inline keyboard buttons as JSON (array of\n                         button rows)\n  --card <json>          Adaptive Card JSON object (when supported by the\n                         channel)\n  --channel <channel>    Channel:\n                         telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|line\n  --components <json>    Discord components payload as JSON\n  --dry-run              Print payload and skip sending (default: false)\n  --force-document       Send media as document to avoid Telegram compression\n                         (Telegram only). Applies to images and GIFs. (default:\n                         false)\n  --gif-playback         Treat video media as GIF playback (WhatsApp only).\n                         (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --interactive <json>   Shared interactive payload as JSON (buttons/selects\n                         rendered natively by supported channels)\n  --json                 Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>   Message body (required unless --media is set)\n  --media <path-or-url>  Attach media (image/audio/video/document). Accepts\n                         local paths or URLs.\n  --reply-to <id>        Reply-to message id\n  --silent               Send message silently without notification (Telegram +\n                         Discord) (default: false)\n  -t, --target <dest>    Recipient/channel: E.164 for WhatsApp/Signal, Telegram\n                         chat id/@username, Discord/Slack channel/user, or\n                         iMessage handle/chat_id\n  --thread-id <id>       Thread id (Telegram forum thread)\n  --verbose              Verbose logging (default: false)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":884,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.28 (f9b1079) — Gateway online—please keep hands, feet, and appendages inside the shell at all times.\n\nUsage: openclaw message send [options]\n\nSend a message\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id (accountId)\n  --buttons <json>       Telegram inline keyboard buttons as JSON (array of\n                         button rows)\n  --card <json>          Adaptive Card JSON object (when supported by the\n                         channel)\n  --channel <channel>    Channel:\n                         telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|line\n  --components <json>    Discord components payload as JSON\n  --dry-run              Print payload and skip sending (default: false)\n  --force-document       Send media as document to avoid Telegram compression\n                         (Telegram only). Applies to images and GIFs. (default:\n                         false)\n  --gif-playback         Treat video media as GIF playback (WhatsApp only).\n                         (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --interactive <json>   Shared interactive payload as JSON (buttons/selects\n                         rendered natively by supported channels)\n  --json                 Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>   Message body (required unless --media is set)\n  --media <path-or-url>  Attach media (image/audio/video/document). Accepts\n                         local paths or URLs.\n  --reply-to <id>        Reply-to message id\n  --silent               Send message silently without notification (Telegram +\n                         Discord) (default: false)\n  -t, --target <dest>    Recipient/channel: E.164 for WhatsApp/Signal, Telegram\n                         chat id/@username, Discord/Slack channel/user, or\n                         iMessage handle/chat_id\n  --thread-id <id>       Thread id (Telegram forum thread)\n  --verbose              Verbose logging (default: false)","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775475119230}}
{"type":"message","id":"2699e308","parentId":"fb0a7d9c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:32:19.674Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The openclaw message send command works. I can use it to send messages. Now let me simplify the push_feishu function to just call `openclaw message send` via subprocess.","thinkingSignature":"70884283902a65d363f967af333f60a120eb6c4535c5941eca8f441be5cf5111"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zgsx2nzd58zz_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_strategy_param_auto_audit.py","old_string":"def push_feishu(report: str, alerts: list[dict]) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"通过 OpenClaw message 工具推送到飞书私聊（张玲）。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        # 构造带告警 emoji 的消息摘要\n        severity_emoji = \"🔴\" if any(a[\"severity\"] == \"HIGH\" for a in alerts) else \"🟡\"\n        summary_lines = [f\"{severity_emoji} 策略参数巡检 | {datetime.now().strftime('%m/%d %H:%M')}\"]\n        for a in alerts:\n            sev = \"🔴\" if a[\"severity\"] == \"HIGH\" else \"🟡\"\n            summary_lines.append(f\"{sev} {a['type']}: {a['message'][:100]}\")\n        summary_lines.append(\"\")\n        summary_lines.append(\"报告文件: strategy_param_auto_audit_YYYYMMDD.md\")\n\n        message_text = \"\\n\".join(summary_lines)\n        # 通过 OpenClaw 内置 message 工具发送\n        import subprocess\n        result = subprocess.run(\n            [\n                sys.executable, \"-c\",\n                f\"\"\"\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '{SCRIPTS_DIR}')\n# 延迟导入避免循环依赖\nfrom run_strategy_param_auto_audit import _send_via_openclaw\n_send_via_openclaw({json.dumps(message_text)!r})\n\"\"\"\n            ],\n            capture_output=True,\n            text=True,\n            timeout=15,\n        )\n        return result.returncode == 0\n    except Exception:\n        return False\n\n\ndef _send_via_openclaw(message: str) -> None:\n    \"\"\"通过 OpenClaw 发送飞书消息（供 subprocess 调用）。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        from pathlib import Path\n        import urllib.request, urllib.error\n\n        # 读取 openclaw.json 中的所有飞书账号配置\n        openclaw_cfg = Path.home() / \".openclaw\" / \"openclaw.json\"\n        data = json.loads(openclaw_cfg.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n        feishu_cfg = data.get(\"channels\", {}).get(\"feishu\", {})\n        accounts = feishu_cfg.get(\"accounts\", {})\n        target_open_id = \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\"\n\n        # 尝试所有 app，找到能发给 target_open_id 的那个\n        tried = []\n        for acc_name, account in accounts.items():\n            app_id = account.get(\"appId\", \"\")\n            app_secret = account.get(\"appSecret\", \"\")\n            if not app_id or not app_secret:\n                continue\n            tried.append(acc_name)\n            try:\n                # 获取 token\n                token_url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\"\n                token_req = urllib.request.Request(\n                    token_url,\n                    data=json.dumps({\"app_id\": app_id, \"app_secret\": app_secret}).encode(\"utf-8\"),\n                    headers={\"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"},\n                )\n                with urllib.request.urlopen(token_req, timeout=8) as resp:\n                    token_result = json.loads(resp.read())\n                if token_result.get(\"code\") != 0:\n                    continue\n                token = token_result[\"tenant_access_token\"]\n\n                # 发消息\n                msg_url = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=open_id\"\n                msg_req = urllib.request.Request(\n                    msg_url,\n                    data=json.dumps({\n                        \"receive_id\": target_open_id,\n                        \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n                        \"content\": {\"text\": message},\n                    }).encode(\"utf-8\"),\n                    headers={\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {token}\", \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"},\n                )\n                with urllib.request.urlopen(msg_req, timeout=8) as resp:\n                    result = json.loads(resp.read())\n                if result.get(\"code\") == 0:\n                    print(f\"OK via {acc_name}\")\n                    return\n            except Exception:\n                pass\n\n        print(f\"Failed, tried: {tried}\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Error: {e}\")","new_string":"def push_feishu(report: str, alerts: list[dict]) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"通过 openclaw message send 命令推送到飞书私聊。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        import subprocess\n\n        # 构造消息摘要\n        severity_emoji = \"🔴\" if any(a[\"severity\"] == \"HIGH\" for a in alerts) else \"🟡\"\n        lines = [f\"{severity_emoji} 策略参数巡检 | {datetime.now().strftime('%m/%d %H:%M')}\"]\n        for a in alerts:\n            sev = \"🔴\" if a[\"severity\"] == \"HIGH\" else \"🟡\"\n            lines.append(f\"{sev} {a['type']}: {a['message'][:100]}\")\n        lines.append(\"\")\n        lines.append(\"报告: research/reports/strategy_param_auto_audit_YYYYMMDD.md\")\n        message_text = \"\\n\".join(lines)\n\n        result = subprocess.run(\n            [\n                \"openclaw\", \"message\", \"send\",\n                \"--channel\", \"feishu\",\n                \"--target\", \"user:ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n                \"--message\", message_text,\n            ],\n            capture_output=True,\n            text=True,\n            timeout=20,\n        )\n        return result.returncode == 0\n    except Exception:\n        return False"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":104511,"output":1287,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127265,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775475119233,"responseId":"0622ccaf3a1e67481591a