{"type":"message","id":"ad09f439","parentId":"95cbce12","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:36:43.319Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The HEARTBEAT.md is empty. I need to add a check for the param_audit_push_flag files. Let me update it to check for these files and push via the message tool if found.","thinkingSignature":"3cd2dcdc683a042696e1faf200184f3f59bdb328985b822fe3c773bfa91db39e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6bymbioyxtkj_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n## Periodic Checks\n\n### 策略参数巡检推送检查\n每30分钟检查一次，发现 `param_audit_push_flag_YYYYMMDD.json` 时，通过飞书推送摘要并删除标记文件。\n\n```python\nimport json, subprocess\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nflag_files = sorted(Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports\").glob(\".param_audit_push_flag_*.json\"))\nif flag_files:\n    latest = flag_files[-1]\n    data = json.loads(latest.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n    msg = data.get(\"message\", \"\")\n    # 使用 openclaw message send 推送（cross-app 问题可忽略，openclaw CLI 会自动处理）\n    r = subprocess.run(\n        [\"openclaw\", \"message\", \"send\", \"--channel\", \"feishu\",\n         \"--target\", \"user:ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n         \"--message\", msg],\n        capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=20,\n    )\n    if r.returncode == 0:\n        latest.unlink()  # 推送成功后删除标记文件\n```\n","file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":94979,"output":355,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116801,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775475393131,"responseId":"0622cdc13cca083ab341be6f0095f9c6"}}
