{"type":"message","id":"99cb6723","parentId":"5fe8246b","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:46:35.602Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what content is being pushed. Let me explain clearly - it's the strategy parameter audit report that we just configured, which will be pushed to Feishu every Saturday at 10:00 AM.","thinkingSignature":"623cfeeab2ad557005cafea955b7eb741b37341a751ec94ba8c5bb7a98035dc3"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 推送的就是这个内容——每周六 10:00 自动触发，推送给你：\n\n```\n🔴 策略参数巡检 | 04/11 10:00\n\n🔴 sharpe_low: Sharpe=-0.388 < 0.8（窗口：2026-01-12 ~ 2026-03-03）\n🔴 annual_low: 年化=-16.82% < 40.0%（窗口：2026-01-12 ~ 2026-03-03）\n🟡 sharpe_drift: Sharpe 漂移告警：均值 1.280，最新 -0.388，下降 1.668\n\n报告: strategy_param_auto_audit_YYYYMMDD.md\n```\n\n**触发条件（有任意一项才推送）：**\n\n| 条件 | 阈值 |\n|------|------|\n| Sharpe 过低 | 最新窗口 Sharpe < 0.8 |\n| 年化过低 | 最新窗口年化收益 < 40% |\n| 回撤过高 | 最新窗口最大回撤 > 12% |\n| Sharpe 漂移 | 较9窗口均值下降 > 0.5 |\n\n**没有告警时**（各项指标正常）→ 不推送，静默运行。\n\n你看刚才我手动推送的那条测试消息收到了吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":319,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":132098,"totalTokens":132491,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775475982475,"responseId":"0622d00f172f4afcae9a62e799cf6d20"}}
