{"type":"message","id":"560f8d2d","parentId":"e5cefbd4","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:50:24.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron was created with an agent task. Now let me test it manually to make sure it works.Actually, I should update the script's push function to NOT try the CLI (which fails), and instead just write the flag file. Then the agent cron will pick it up and use the message tool to push directly.\n\nActually, let me simplify the script's push function. Since we're now using an agent-based cron that can use the message tool directly, the push_feishu function just needs to write the flag file, and the agent will handle the actual sending.Wait, but the agent cron will run the script AND handle the push via instructions. Let me simplify the script to just write the report and NOT try any push (since the CLI push fails anyway). The agent will read the report and push via message tool.Actually, let me re-think. The new cron is an agent-based job. When it fires:\n\n\n1. It gets the message instructing it to run the script and send the alert via Feishu if needed\n2. The script writes the report and flag file (the push will fail since CLI can't send to this open_id)\n3. The agent reads the flag file and sends via message tool\n\nBut this is inefficient—I'm doing the push twice. I should just have the script write the report without attempting the push, then let the agent handle the entire push workflow when it reads the flag file. Let me update the script's push function to skip the CLI push and let the agent do it all.","thinkingSignature":"814bd19888a5e2d6da01e50a3fbb7fe19a5191ec015eecb36a9e194e81e82c47"},{"type":"text","text":"Agent cron 创建成功 ✅ 现在更新脚本——既然用 agent 模式跑了，就不需要脚本自己推送了（CLI 跨 app 限制），由 agent 读取报告后用 message 工具发：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8ifhub8o6dl6_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_strategy_param_auto_audit.py","old_string":"def push_feishu(report: str, alerts: list[dict]) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"\n    通过 openclaw message send（飞书 native 推送）。\n    若 open_id cross app 失败（跨 app 账号问题），写入标记文件供主 session 检测并推送。\n    \"\"\"\n    import subprocess\n\n    date_tag = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    flag_path = REPORT_DIR / f\".param_audit_push_flag_{date_tag}.json\"\n\n    severity_emoji = \"🔴\" if any(a[\"severity\"] == \"HIGH\" for a in alerts) else \"🟡\"\n    lines = [f\"{severity_emoji} 策略参数巡检 | {datetime.now().strftime('%m/%d %H:%M')}\"]\n    for a in alerts:\n        sev = \"🔴\" if a[\"severity\"] == \"HIGH\" else \"🟡\"\n        lines.append(f\"{sev} {a['type']}: {a['message'][:100]}\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(f\"报告: strategy_param_auto_audit_{date_tag}.md\")\n    message_text = \"\\n\".join(lines)\n\n    # 尝试 openclaw message send\n    result = subprocess.run(\n        [\"openclaw\", \"message\", \"send\",\n         \"--channel\", \"feishu\",\n         \"--target\", \"user:ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n         \"--message\", message_text],\n        capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=20,\n    )\n\n    if result.returncode == 0:\n        return True\n\n    # 失败（跨 app 问题）：写入标记文件，供主 session 的 heartbeat 检测并推送\n    flag_path.write_text(\n        json.dumps({\"message\": message_text, \"alerts\": alerts, \"written_at\": datetime.now().isoformat()}),\n        encoding=\"utf-8\",\n    )\n    return False","new_string":"def push_feishu(report: str, alerts: list[dict]) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"\n    推送逻辑由 agent cron 负责。\n    脚本只负责写报告文件和标记文件，agent 读取后用 message 工具推送到飞书私聊。\n    \"\"\"\n    date_tag = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    flag_path = REPORT_DIR / f\".param_audit_push_flag_{date_tag}.json\"\n\n    severity_emoji = \"🔴\" if any(a[\"severity\"] == \"HIGH\" for a in alerts) else \"🟡\"\n    lines = [f\"{severity_emoji} 策略参数巡检 | {datetime.now().strftime('%m/%d %H:%M')}\"]\n    for a in alerts:\n        sev = \"🔴\" if a[\"severity\"] == \"HIGH\" else \"🟡\"\n        lines.append(f\"{sev} {a['type']}: {a['message'][:100]}\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(f\"报告: strategy_param_auto_audit_{date_tag}.md\")\n\n    flag_path.write_text(\n        json.dumps({\"message\": \"\\n\".join(lines), \"alerts\": alerts, \"written_at\": datetime.now().isoformat()}),\n        encoding=\"utf-8\",\n    )\n    return True  # 标记文件写好，agent cron 会处理推送"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108185,"output":1119,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130771,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775476198826,"responseId":"0622d0e74c2a2740b132d72625d2b25f"}}
