{"type":"message","id":"b2f30c60","parentId":"be9981ae","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:51:16.647Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me summarize the final setup:1. Agent cron: `strategy-param-audit-feishu` - runs every Saturday 10:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai) as an isolated session with the coding-agent\n   - When it fires, it will:     a. Run the Python script to generate the report\n     b. The script writes the report + flag file\n     c. The agent reads the flag file and uses the message tool to send to `ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae`2. Backup mechanism: HEARTBEAT.md - every 30 minutes, if there are flag files remaining (in case the agent cron fails), I'm notified and can send manually3. \n\nI'm ready to summarize this for the user.","thinkingSignature":"566410dea8e762fceec58f9efff4f7e6a966c3ccc11303e9036e842088a1fcb7"},{"type":"text","text":"收到了吗？这是今天巡检的完整推送链路说明：\n\n**每周六 10:00（节后首个交易日不休）**\n\n```\nPython 脚本生成报告\n        ↓\n标记文件（.param_audit_push_flag）\n        ↓\nAgent Cron 检测到标记文件\n        ↓\nmessage 工具 → 飞书私聊给你推送 🔴 告警摘要\n```\n\n**推送目标**：`user:ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae`（你现在这个私聊）\n\n**触发条件**（有任意一项才推）：\n- Sharpe < 0.8\n- 年化收益 < 40%\n- 回撤 > 12%\n- Sharpe 漂移 > 0.5\n\n**无告警则静默**，不打扰。\n\n另外，之前 crontab 里加的那个 `0 10 * * 6`（直接跑 Python 脚本的）保留还是删掉？现在有了 Agent Cron 双重保险，可以把 crontab 那个删了避免重复。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":105501,"output":392,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127360,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775476264426,"responseId":"0622d128cc39d7e2664fa1f741abc835"}}
