{"type":"message","id":"4196da78","parentId":"38fecfda","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:55:21.861Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The Agent Cron is set up correctly. Now let me understand what happened to the system crontab.\n\nLooking at the launchd plists:\n- `com.ling.daily-exec-card.plist` - possibly the daily actionable brief\n- `com.ling.daily-position-report.plist` - daily position report\n\nThese are managed by launchd, not crontab. The `crontab -l` entries I saw earlier might have been leftovers from before or I might have misread something.\n\nActually, let me check if the install scripts for the things I thought were in crontab actually install to crontab or launchd:","thinkingSignature":"f76e1a86766532ca605753b68412fe81baff9b7d7e663288d64085afe5ad9d0f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dc0e8qlyfcjk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/install_investment_research_guard_cron.sh 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"launchd\\|crontab\\|plist\" | head -10; echo \"---\"; ls /Users/ling/Library/LaunchAgents/ 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"invest\\|research\\|paper\\|breath\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":108987,"output":238,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130692,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775476510241,"responseId":"0622d21e05e12b8bb820d51ab892a5c1"}}
