{"type":"message","id":"fed9dd61","parentId":"95a0d294","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:32:22.312Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now create the OpenClaw agent cron. The agent should:\n1. Read the context file prepared by the Python script\n2. Generate 3-5 strategy hypotheses\n3. Write them to the hypothesis markdown file\n4. If there's a significant finding, push to Feishu\n\nLet me design the cron message carefully.","thinkingSignature":"fcb4d44ddaad57c130b60cd1940f4d3c20e6a7dbc5cba443630628279594d12b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cejun1hpudi5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"strategy-hypothesis-weekly\" \\\n  --cron \"0 16 * * 6\" \\\n  --tz \"Asia/Shanghai\" \\\n  --agent \"coding-agent\" \\\n  --session \"isolated\" \\\n  --timeout-seconds 180 \\\n  --message \"运行策略假设周度生成任务：\n\n步骤1: 读取上下文文件\nls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/.hypothesis_context_*.txt | sort | tail -1\n读取该文件内容，理解近期 walk-forward 结果、模拟盘表现、简报摘要\n\n步骤2: 生成策略假设\n基于上下文，生成 3~5 条具体、可验证的策略假设，写成 Markdown 格式，包含：\n- 假设描述（清晰、具体）\n- 数据支撑（引用上下文中的具体数字）\n- 验证方法（建议如何测试这个假设）\n\n步骤3: 保存结果\n写入文件: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/hypothesis/YYYYMMDD_hypotheses.md\n日期用今天（如 20260411）。格式：Markdown，含标题、日期、假设列表。\n\n步骤4: 推送\n如有重大发现（如策略系统性失效、发现新的盈利模式、参数严重漂移），通过飞书私聊推送：\nopenclaw message send --channel feishu --target user:ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae --message \\\"🧠 策略假设周报 | 今天日期\\n\\n⚠️ 重大发现：...\\\"\\n\\n完成后输出：已完成，生成 X 条假设，文件路径：...\" \\\n  2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":107865,"output":463,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129795,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775478725556,"responseId":"0622dac60e827d71d93e538bf225db02"}}
