n    \"expr\": \"0 16 * * 6\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"运行策略假设周度生成任务：\\n\\n步骤1: 读取上下文文件\\nls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/.hypothesis_context_*.txt | sort | tail -1\\n读取该文件内容，理解近期 walk-forward 结果、模拟盘表现、简报摘要\\n\\n步骤2: 生成策略假设\\n基于上下文，生成 3~5 条具体、可验证的策略假设，写成 Markdown 格式，包含：\\n- 假设描述（清晰、具体）\\n- 数据支撑（引用上下文中的具体数字）\\n- 验证方法（建议如何测试这个假设）\\n\\n步骤3: 保存结果\\n写入文件: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/hypothesis/YYYYMMDD_hypotheses.md\\n日期用今天（如 20260411）。格式：Markdown，含标题、日期、假设列表。\\n\\n步骤4: 推送\\n如有重大发现（如策略系统性失效、发现新的盈利模式、参数严重漂移），通过飞书私聊推送：\\nopenclaw message send --channel feishu --target user:ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae --message \\\"🧠 策略假设周报 | 今天日期\\\\n\\\\n⚠️ 重大发现：...\\\"\\\\n\\\\n完成后输出：已完成，生成 X 条假设，文件路径：...\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 180\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"last\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1775894400000\n  }\n}","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775478743313}}
{"type":"message","id":"5ffa04ec","parentId":"a8ca0c45","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:32:36.495Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great! The agent cron is created. Now let me also test running the Python script to generate the context file. Let me also think about the scheduling - Saturday 16:00 makes sense. But wait - should the Python script run as a cron too, or does the agent cron handle everything?\n\nLooking at the setup:\n- The OpenClaw agent cron (Saturday 16:00) runs the Python script first to generate context, then the agent reads the context and generates hypotheses.\n\nActually, let me reconsider. The Python script and the agent cron should be merged. The OpenClaw agent should:1. Run the Python script to generate context\n\n\n2. Read the context file\n3. Generate hypotheses\n4. Write to markdown\n5. Push if needed\n\nSo I should make the Python script a simple context builder, and the agent cron handles everything. But the Python script also needs to be run as part of the agent cron. Actually, the OpenClaw agent cron message can include running the Python script and then reading its output. Let me update the cron message to reflect this.","thinkingSignature":"eb1f40e380b9563df995a1c7b7f3dcd546587e001aac866afacfbc5c93f0f77c"},{"type":"text","text":"周六 16:00 的 Agent Cron 已创建 ✅\n\n现在测试一下 Python 上下文生成脚本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cbee8xi0y9gg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && python3 scripts/run_strategy_hypothesis_weekly.py 2>&1 | head -40"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":107531,"output":307,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129305,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775478743317,"responseId":"0622dad8fb8ff95997c9a4310ff8f39d"}}
