{"type":"message","id":"02be828e","parentId":"8b821c87","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:33:21.474Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now also fix the walk-forward Sharpe issue. The summary JSON has the Sharpe data at the window level in the windows array, but the script uses the wrong field name. Let me check the aggressive_walkforward_summary JSON structure more carefully.\n\nActually, looking at the earlier output:\n- The summary JSON has `windows` with `test_sharpe_daily` field\n- But the summary section also has `mean_test_sharpe_daily` and `last_window` or similar\n\nLet me also fix the walk-forward loading to use the correct fields from the summary JSON.","thinkingSignature":"dbad237097f77ce89cae20651424d48b03f11e469ebcccc771d0f979dd31a000"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9tihtmltm9dt_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_strategy_hypothesis_weekly.py","old_string":"    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"## 3. 简报摘要\")\n    brief = load_brief_summary()\n    lines.append(brief[\"summary\"][:1500])","new_string":"    # Walk-forward 窗口级数据（从 windows CSV）\n    wf_csv = REPORT_DIR / wf_path.name.replace(\"summary\", \"windows\")\n    if wf_csv.exists():\n        try:\n            import pandas as pd\n            wfdf = pd.read_csv(wf_csv)\n            wfdf = wfdf.sort_values(\"test_end\")\n            last3 = wfdf.tail(3)\n            lines.append(\"\")\n            lines.append(\"最近3个窗口（从CSV）:\")\n            for _, row in last3.iterrows():\n                lines.append(f\"  {row.get('test_start','?')} ~ {row.get('test_end','?')}: Sharpe={row.get('test_sharpe_daily','?')}, 年化={row.get('test_annual_pct','?')}%\")\n        except Exception:\n            pass"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":107412,"output":395,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129274