{"type":"message","id":"8a558e8a","parentId":"81d4716f","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:05:26.705Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hpc78xj2gdr4_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"获取可转债申购列表\n    Parameters\n    --------\n    retry_count : int, 默认 3\n                 如遇网络等问题重复执行的次数 \n    pause : int, 默认 0\n                重复请求数据过程中暂停的秒数，防止请求间隔时间太短出现的问题\n    \n    Return\n    ------\n    DataFrame\n    bcode:债券代码\n    bname:债券名称\n    scode:股票代码\n    sname:股票名称\n    xcode:申购代码\n    amount:发行总数(亿元)\n    marketprice:最新市场价格\n    convprice:转股价格\n    firstdayprice:首日收盘价\n    ipo_date:上网发行日期\n    issue_date:上市日期\n    ballot:中签率(%)\n    return：打新收益率(%)\n    perreturn:每中一股收益（万元）"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":334,"aggregated":"获取可转债申购列表\n    Parameters\n    --------\n    retry_count : int, 默认 3\n                 如遇网络等问题重复执行的次数 \n    pause : int, 默认 0\n                重复请求数据过程中暂停的秒数，防止请求间隔时间太短出现的问题\n    \n    Return\n    ------\n    DataFrame\n    bcode:债券代码\n    bname:债券名称\n    scode:股票代码\n    sname:股票名称\n    xcode:申购代码\n    amount:发行总数(亿元)\n    marketprice:最新市场价格\n    convprice:转股价格\n    firstdayprice:首日收盘价\n    ipo_date:上网发行日期\n    issue_date:上市日期\n    ballot:中签率(%)\n    return：打新收益率(%)\n    perreturn:每中一股收益（万元）","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775480726702}}
{"type":"message","id":"6592b018","parentId":"8a558e8a","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:05:39.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`new_cbonds` only provides new bond issuance data (可转债申购列表), not historical market data for existing convertible bonds. This is for IPO/new bond subscriptions, not trading data.\n\nLet me check if there are other data sources for convertible bond market data. Let me look at what else tushare provides.","thinkingSignature":"b48d143a9680edfec4e7e15fa7636dbd2d5972563a883e7f000a9992ab422d47"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d1ja34j6hpfm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\n# 列出所有数据接口\nprint('=== tushare 可用数据接口 ===')\nfuncs = [f for f in dir(ts) if not f.startswith('_')]\nfor f in sorted(funcs):\n    if any(kw in f.lower() for kw in ['cb', 'bond', 'convertible', '转债', '转债']):\n        print(f'  {f}')\nprint()\n# 也查一下 pro 接口\ntry:\n    pro = ts.pro_api()\n    funcs_pro = [f for f in dir(pro) if any(kw in f.lower() for kw in ['cb', 'bond', 'convert'])]\n    print('=== pro API 可转债相关 ===')\n    for f in funcs_pro:\n        print(f'  {f}')\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f'pro API error: {e}')\n\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":111548,"output":282,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133297,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775480726706,"responseId":"0622e29728406d5d286c38049b7a1e03"}}
