{"type":"message","id":"1e7029e8","parentId":"64a02493","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:07:12.574Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The current tushare setup only downloads daily market data (股票日行情) and index data. There's no convertible bond data being downloaded.\n\nLet me now tell the user about the findings:\n\n1. The existing tushare token doesn't work for the pro API (which would have comprehensive convertible bond data)\n2. The regular tushare `new_cbonds()` only provides new bond IPO data, not historical market data\n3. The current system doesn't have convertible bond data\n\nFor convertible bond research, we would need:\n- A valid tushare pro token (the current one is invalid)\n- Access to cb_daily (可转债日线行情), cb_basic (可转债基本信息), etc.\n\n\n- Given the token and network limitations, I should look into alternative free data sources like jqdata or akshare to see if we can pull convertible bond information.","thinkingSignature":"45335049ff81547c8edabe0703e229c3955ea306b6b1dad9417b2a98e83522f1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z717pzopkeau_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport akshare as ak\n# 查可转债数据接口\nfuncs = [f for f in dir(ak) if 'cb' in f.lower() or 'bond' in f.lower() or '转债' in f.lower()]\nprint('akshare 可转债相关接口:')\nfor f in funcs[:20]:\n    print(f'  {f}')\n\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":110455,"output":286,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132208,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775480818483,"responseId":"0622e2f30cc29aadede66e1a7c9f4ae4"}}
