{"type":"message","id":"15c01347","parentId":"c845a2e9","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:08:20.285Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2ucl81ymo7u3_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"数据更新到: 2026-04-03\n转债数量: 343\n平均双低值: 204.96\n平均溢价率: 53.34 %\n平均价格: 151.622\n平均转股价值: 95.89\n到期收益率: -11.47 %\n市场温度: 82.89\n\n=== 结论 ===\n可以构建的可转债策略：\n1. 双低策略: avg_dblow < X 时买入\n2. 低溢价策略: avg_premium_rt < Y 时\n3. 债底保护: avg_price < 105 时价值凸显\n4. 市场温度: temperature > 80 时减仓"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":911,"aggregated":"数据更新到: 2026-04-03\n转债数量: 343\n平均双低值: 204.96\n平均溢价率: 53.34 %\n平均价格: 151.622\n平均转股价值: 95.89\n到期收益率: -11.47 %\n市场温度: 82.89\n\n=== 结论 ===\n可以构建的可转债策略：\n1. 双低策略: avg_dblow < X 时买入\n2. 低溢价策略: avg_premium_rt < Y 时\n3. 债底保护: avg_price < 105 时价值凸显\n4. 市场温度: temperature > 80 时减仓","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775480900281}}
{"type":"message","id":"31f1d783","parentId":"15c01347","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:08:47.905Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great data! Now let me summarize my findings for the user:1. **akshare 集思录可转债指数** - Live data, updated to yesterday (2026-04-03)\n   - Market temperature, avg price, avg premium, double-low indicator, YTM\n   - Great for market timing and broad strategy research\n\n2. **akshare 集思录可转债实时概况** (`bond_cb_jsl`) - 30 convertible bonds\n   - Real-time data including price, premium, stock price, ratings, etc.\n   - Good for picking individual bonds\n\n3. **Individual bond history** - The `bond_zh_hs_cov_daily` only goes to 2021, so that's not useful for live trading.\n\nThe key challenge for a full convertible bond strategy is accessing historical daily data for individual bonds rather than just aggregate market-level data.\n\nFor now, I can use the market-level index from akshare as an overlay signal to time when small-cap stocks might outperform, since the market temperature and premium indicators could serve as useful macro signals for the small-cap strategy.\n\nNow I'm drafting a response for the user.","thinkingSignature":"57de78cf6a0ab933833723cdbb5a0773687b559f432a9ae65b12c7ca888d5d36"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好消息，akshare 集思录可转债数据是活的，更新到昨天。\n\n---\n\n**现有数据情况：**\n\n| 数据源 | 内容 | 更新频率 | 是否可用 |\n|--------|------|---------|---------|\n| akshare `bond_cb_jsl` | 集思录可转债实时概况（30只） | 实时 | ✅ 可用 |\n| akshare `bond_cb_index_jsl` | 可转债市场指数历史（200+指标） | 日频，更新到昨天 | ✅ 可用 |\n| akshare `bond_zh_hs_cov_daily` | 全市场可转债日线 | 只有到2021年的历史 | ❌ 太旧 |\n| tushare pro `cb_daily` | 可转债日线历史 | 日频 | ❌ token失效 |\n\n---\n\n**可以做的研究（不需要历史日线）：**\n\n**1. 市场温度/情绪指标**（最快落地）\n把集思录可转债市场温度（temperature）和你的小市值策略结合起来——当可转债市场温度 > 80 时，说明市场整体风险偏好高，小市值策略胜率更高。这个可以作为你现有 breadth signal 的补充。\n\n**2. 双低策略回测**\n用集思录的历史指数数据（250天），验证\"双低值 < 180 时买入\"是否有效。\n\n**3. ETF套利数据**\nakshare 也有 ETF 溢价率数据（`fund_etf_hist_em`），不需要实时速度，可以研究 ETF 折溢价的规律作为辅助信号。\n\n---\n\n**建议**：先把**可转债市场温度**作为因子加进周度假设生成里，这个最快能落地。需要我写个脚本把集思录数据拉进来吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":111530,"output":595,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133592,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775480900286,"responseId":"0622e34553d083eb24fe53ecdc23ca70"}}
{"type":"message","id":"458b774a","parentId":"31f1d783","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:10:17.080Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b520f45b3d0a0c245f9db7d6486d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-06 21:10 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b520f45b3d0a0c245f9db7d6486d]\n张玲: 好"}],"timestamp":1775481017064}}
{"type":"message","id":"223e5763","parentId":"458b774a","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:10:59.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a script to pull in the JSL convertible bond market temperature data and integrate it into the weekly hypothesis generation. Let me create a script that fetches the data and adds it to the weekly context.","thinkingSignature":"d4815ba415f06129c1fcf662884d3b7375d5d572db656646f648e1299a6dd59c"},{"type":"text","text":"好，写个脚本把集思录可转债数据常态化：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bg62cgmaq8sg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/fetch_cb_market_temperature.py << 'PYEOF'\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n每天定时抓取集思录可转债市场数据，写入 reports/cb_market_YYYYMMDD.json\n用于：周度假设生成（可转债市场温度作为小市值策略的辅助信号）\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\nCB_DATA_DIR = REPORT_DIR / \"cb_data\"\nCB_DATA_DIR.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\n\ndef fetch_jsl_cb_index() -> dict:\n    \"\"\"抓取集思录可转债市场指数数据。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        import akshare as ak\n        df = ak.bond_cb_index_jsl()\n        latest = df.iloc[-1].to_dict()\n        # 历史20天趋势\n        hist = df.tail(20).to_dict(\"records\")\n        return {\n            \"ok\": True,\n            \"index_date\": str(latest.get(\"price_dt\", \"\")),\n            \"price\": float(latest.get(\"price\", 0)),\n            \"increase_rt\": float(latest.get(\"increase_rt\", 0)),\n            \"avg_price\": float(latest.get(\"avg_price\", 0)),\n            \"mid_convert_value\": float(latest.get(\"mid_convert_value\", 0)),\n            \"avg_dblow\": float(latest.get(\"avg_dblow\", 0)),\n            \"avg_premium_rt\": float(latest.get(\"avg_premium_rt\", 0)),\n            \"avg_ytm_rt\": float(latest.get(\"avg_ytm_rt\", 0)),\n            \"temperature\": float(latest.get(\"temperature\", 0)),\n            \"count\": int(latest.get(\"count\", 0)),\n            \"turnover_rt\": float(latest.get(\"turnover_rt\", 0)),\n            \"price_90_100\": float(latest.get(\"price_90_100\", 0)),\n            \"price_100_110\": float(latest.get(\"price_100_110\", 0)),\n            \"price_110_120\": float(latest.get(\"price_110_120\", 0)),\n            \"price_120_130\": float(latest.get(\"price_120_130\", 0)),\n            \"price_130\": float(latest.get(\"price_130\", 0)),\n            \"hist_20d\": hist,\n        }\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"ok\": False, \"error\": str(e)}\n\n\ndef fetch_jsl_cb_snapshot() -> dict:\n    \"\"\"抓取集思录可转债实时概况（按双低排序）。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        import akshare as ak\n        df = ak.bond_cb_jsl()\n        # 取双低最小的10只\n        df_sorted = df.sort_values(\"双低\").head(10)\n        return {\n            \"ok\": True,\n            \"date\": str(df[\"代码\"].iloc[0]),  # 无日期字段，取第一条的时间戳\n            \"top10_low_db\": [\n                {\n                    \"code\": str(r[\"代码\"]),\n                    \"name\": str(r[\"转债名称\"]),\n                    \"price\": float(r[\"现价\"]),\n                    \"convert_premium\": float(r[\"转股溢价率\"]),\n                    \"dblow\": float(r[\"双低\"]),\n                    \"rating\": str(r[\"债券评级\"]),\n                    \"stock_code\": str(r[\"正股代码\"]),\n                    \"stock_name\": str(r[\"正股名称\"]),\n                }\n                for _, r in df_sorted.iterrows()\n            ],\n            \"total_count\": len(df),\n        }\n    except Exception as e:\n        return {\"ok\": False, \"error\": str(e)}\n\n\ndef signal_interpretation(data: dict) -> str:\n    \"\"\"把数据翻译成对小市值策略的信号。\"\"\"\n    temp = data.get(\"temperature\", 50)\n    dblow = data.get(\"avg_dblow\", 200)\n    avg_premium = data.get(\"avg_premium_rt\", 50)\n    avg_price = data.get(\"avg_price\", 150)\n    ytm = data.get(\"avg_ytm_rt\", 0)\n    count = data.get(\"count\", 0)\n\n    signals = []\n    risk_level = \"🟢\"\n\n    # 市场温度\n    if temp >= 80:\n        signals.append(f\"⚠️ 可转债市场温度{temp:.0f}（历史高位），风险偏好高但注意债市回调风险\")\n        risk_level = \"🔴\"\n    elif temp <= 30:\n        signals.append(f\"🟡 可转债市场温度{temp:.0f}（历史低位），关注超跌反弹机会\")\n    else:\n        signals.append(f\"✅ 可转债市场温度{temp:.0f}（中性区间）\")\n\n    # 双低值\n    if dblow < 180:\n        signals.append(f\"✅ 平均双低值{dblow:.1f}（偏低，市场整体偏低估，适合布局\")\n        risk_level = \"🟢\"\n    elif dblow > 220:\n        signals.append(f\"🔴 平均双低值{dblow:.1f}（偏高，市场整体偏高，注意仓位控制\")\n        risk_level = \"🔴\"\n    else:\n        signals.append(f\"⚪ 平均双低值{dblow:.1f}（中性区间）\")\n\n    # 溢价率\n    if avg_premium < 20:\n        signals.append(f\"✅ 平均溢价率{avg_premium:.1f}%（偏低，股性强，适合偏股型策略\")\n    elif avg_premium > 60:\n        signals.append(f\"⚠️ 平均溢价率{avg_premium:.1f}%（偏高，债性强，对小市值信号敏感度降低）\")\n\n    # 到期收益率\n    if ytm > -3:\n        signals.append(f\"✅ 到期收益率{ytm:.1f}%（债底保护较强，下行空间有限）\")\n    else:\n        signals.append(f\"⚠️ 到期收益率{ytm:.1f}%（债底保护弱，注意信用风险）\")\n\n    # 成交额（活跃度）\n    turnover = data.get(\"turnover_rt\", 0)\n    if turnover < 5:\n        signals.append(f\"⚠️ 换手率{turnover:.1f}%偏低，市场活跃度不足\")\n    else:\n        signals.append(f\"✅ 换手率{turnover:.1f}%，市场活跃度正常\")\n\n    return \"\\n\".join(signals)\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    date_tag = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    print(f\"[{datetime.now():%Y-%m-%d %H:%M}] 抓取可转债市场数据...\")\n\n    index_data = fetch_jsl_cb_index()\n    snapshot_data = fetch_jsl_cb_snapshot()\n\n    result = {\n        \"fetched_at\": datetime.now().isoformat(),\n        \"date_tag\": date_tag,\n        \"cb_index\": index_data,\n        \"cb_snapshot\": snapshot_data,\n        \"signal\": signal_interpretation(index_data) if index_data.get(\"ok\") else \"数据抓取失败\",\n    }\n\n    # 写入每日数据文件\n    out_path = CB_DATA_DIR / f\"cb_market_{date_tag}.json\"\n    out_path.write_text(json.dumps(result, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    print(f\"已保存: {out_path}\")\n\n    # 更新最新数据软链接\n    latest_path = CB_DATA_DIR / \"cb_market_latest.json\"\n    latest_path.write_text(json.dumps(result, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    if index_data.get(\"ok\"):\n        print(f\"\\n=== 可转债市场信号 ===\")\n        print(result[\"signal\"])\n        print(f\"\\n转债数量: {index_data.get('count', '?')}\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"\\n抓取失败: {index_data.get('error')}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\nPYEOF\necho \"脚本创建完成\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":1828,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":114046,"totalTokens":137415,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775481017068,"responseId":"0622e3baedd4322f897bd58744d0206c"}}
