{"type":"message","id":"d6a63a9f","parentId":"c485e1c2","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:12:31.546Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great, committed. Now let me give a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"8708da73b7e8ed4cbd501d20bc34c903eb060d44165be70845a8c990d7ab57fa"},{"type":"text","text":"今天关于可转债的事总结一下：\n\n---\n\n**今天做的：**\n- ✅ 确认 akshare 集思录数据是活的，更新到昨天\n- ✅ 写好 `fetch_cb_market_temperature.py`（抓取+信号解读）\n- ✅ 整合进周度假设上下文\n- ✅ 每天 **15:30** 盘后自动抓取 cron 已设置\n\n**今天的可转债市场信号：**\n- 温度 83（历史高位）⚠️\n- 双低值 205（中性）\n- 溢价率 53%（偏高，债性强）\n- 到期收益率 -11.5%（债底保护弱）\n- 换手率正常 ✅\n\n---\n\n**可转债下一步**：等数据积累几周后，可以把\"双低值 < 180 + 温度 < 50\"作为一个独立策略假设，放进周度假设生成里跑回测验证。\n\n今天真的可以休息了 😄"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":114971,"output":214,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136652,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775481143123,"responseId":"0622e43770b990e2da6008694fbd71c0"}}
