{"type":"message","id":"a19658b5","parentId":"806951fb","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:14:13.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found some interesting ones:\n- `fund_etf_spot_em`: ETF实时行情（溢价率、折价率等）\n- `fund_etf_scale_sse` / `fund_etf_scale_szse`: ETF规模变化（机构申购赎回数据）\n\n\n- `fund_etf_fund_daily_em`: ETF基金每日数据\n\nI should examine the spot data with premium and discount rates, and also look into the flow metrics since there's nothing directly labeled as \"flow\" but the SSE/SZSE scale data might contain the information I need.","thinkingSignature":"df8c46443b81bc18ba850b8d4677e7578e36a401b693f281a9fd86a8e2889243"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jtp4bspfhkso_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport akshare as ak\n# ETF实时行情（含溢价率）\ntry:\n    df = ak.fund_etf_spot_em()\n    print('fund_etf_spot_em OK:', len(df), 'rows')\n    print('Columns:', list(df.columns))\n    # 找溢价率相关的列\n    prem_cols = [c for c in df.columns if '溢价' in c or '折价' in c or 'premium' in c.lower() or 'discount' in c.lower()]\n    print('溢价相关列:', prem_cols)\n    print()\n    print(df[['基金代码','基金简称','最新价','涨跌幅','溢价率','折价率','成交量','成交额']].head(10).to_string())\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print('Error:', type(e).__name__, str(e)[:200])\n\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":116053,"output":331,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137851,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775481239597,"responseId":"0622e498c13756ae7aa607c551e0adab"}}
