{"type":"message","id":"052afcfc","parentId":"2b721cc4","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:18:41.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the current pre-market report. It has:\n1. Overall status (BLOCK/FULL_HALT)\n2. Data freshness checks\n3. Paper portfolio performance table\n4. Detailed holdings for each portfolio\n\nWhat needs to be optimized? Let me think about what could be improved:\n1. The report is for 2026-04-02 but generated today (2026-04-06) - the `trade_date_tag` doesn't match today because today is a holiday\n2. The v4_3_aggressive paper profile isn't shown yet - it's a new addition\n3. The holdings don't have full company names (just codes)\n\n\n4. The BLOCK status with journal_missing is confusing for a holiday, and the report is too dense with 8 portfolios when we should focus on just v4_3_aggressive\n\nI should ask what specific improvements they want, since I can't see the interactive card they're referring to.","thinkingSignature":"c38dcf1a7f1de810a05b7a95fa74a34eb79628879a1edb1a37eed2a333c81b85"},{"type":"text","text":"看了现在盘前报告的格式，有几个明显问题：\n\n**当前报告的问题：**\n1. 今天是清明节假期，报告却显示 `trade_date=20260402`，日期混乱\n2. **v4_3_aggressive 模拟盘没有出现**（刚加入，还不在面板配置里）\n3. 持仓只有股票代码，没有公司名称\n4. 8个组合混在一起，重点不突出\n5. BLOCK 原因 `journal_missing` 在非交易日没有意义\n\n你说的\"优化\"是指哪方面？\n\n- **内容上**：加 v4.3 模拟盘？加可转债市场温度？\n- **格式上**：更精简？突出重点？\n- **时间上**：清明节这种非交易日要不要出报告？\n\n卡片内容我看不到，能描述一下你希望盘前报告长什么样吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":115674,"output":367,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137508,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775481500232,"responseId":"0622e59d7158ee01c06a629a1e54600b"}}
