{"type":"message","id":"7738d262","parentId":"04c8a2e0","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:28:40.127Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_thtw06644no4_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        \"\",\n        \"## 7. 时间型验收未闭环项\",\n        *build_watchlist_lines(payload),\n        \"\",\n        \"## 8. 关键证据文件\",\n    ]\n    required = ((payload.get(\"source_files\") or {}).get(\"required\") or {})\n    optional = ((payload.get(\"source_files\") or {}).get(\"optional\") or {})\n    lines.extend(build_source_lines(required, prefix=\"required\"))\n    lines.extend(build_source_lines(optional, prefix=\"optional\"))\n    return \"\\n\".join(lines).strip() + \"\\n\"\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"Render markdown daily quant analysis report from structured JSON\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--input\", default=str(REPORT_DIR / \"daily_quant_analysis_skill_latest.json\"))\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    input_path = Path(args.input)\n    payload = load_json(input_path)\n    trade_date_tag = str(payload.get(\"trade_date_tag\") or \"latest\")\n    markdown = render_markdown(payload)\n\n    outputs = [\n        REPORT_DIR / f\"daily_quant_analysis_skill_{trade_date_tag}.md\",\n        REPORT_DIR / \"daily_quant_analysis_skill_latest.md\",\n        REPORT_DIR / f\"daily_investment_research_brief_{trade_date_tag}.md\",\n        REPORT_DIR / \"daily_investment_research_brief_latest.md\",\n    ]\n    for path in outputs:\n\n[7 more lines in file. Use offset=250 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775482120115}}
{"type":"message","id":"6aebedbc","parentId":"7738d262","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:28:49.832Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the structure. I need to add the new sections to the `render_markdown` function. The sections are numbered, so I need to insert the new CB and v4.3 sections in the right place. Let me add them before the \"7. 时间型验收未闭环项\" section. \n\nBut actually, to make this cleaner, let me just add the new sections before section 7 and after section 6. Let me do a targeted edit.\n\nAlso, I need to add the two helper functions `render_cb_market_section` and `render_v4_3_strategy_section` before the `render_markdown` function, and then call them from `render_markdown`.\n\n\nI'll go with targeted edits to keep this simple.","thinkingSignature":"923ee1e1c796cdf8ef0b32f82a0f06c3a87e7a97f89de21375bbfb7f40206318"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e7eyzip1zguq_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/render_daily_quant_analysis_md.py","old_string":"        \"\",\n        \"## 7. 时间型验收未闭环项\",","new_string":"        \"\",\n        \"## 6.5 🌡️ 可转债市场（集思录）\",\n        render_cb_market_section(payload),\n        \"\",\n        \"## 6.6 📊 当前实盘基准（小市值筹码v4.3进取型）\",\n        render_v4_3_strategy_section(payload),\n        \"\",\n        \"## 7. 时间型验收未闭环项\","}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117770,"output":323,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139560,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775482120131,"responseId":"0622e8084022197d19cf6ca1eb7a3b53"}}
