{"type":"message","id":"c3c3ac50","parentId":"71ff6940","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:35:20.184Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No trading day awareness in `aggregate_intelligence_brief.py`. This means it runs every day, including holidays, and generates reports with wrong dates. Let me add trading day awareness.","thinkingSignature":"ccbfa6e38b58c93236d3c3eca21d4592c2ca31e7ce8472e3c41a1bb58212b413"},{"type":"text","text":"这个脚本也需要加交易日判断。先找到 main 函数：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_08pyqmrh9ma2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"def main\\|sys.argv\\|if __name__\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/aggregate_intelligence_brief.py | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":124611,"output":109,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146187,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775482514712,"responseId":"0622e993a413fe9c77ab344a7fd0be61"}}
