{"type":"message","id":"a8c62dc3","parentId":"56e51095","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:39:56.798Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0084mic5df6i_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport html\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\n\nfrom generate_dashboard_portal import write_dashboard_portal  # type: ignore\nfrom generate_paper_trading_dashboard import (  # type: ignore\n    as_records,\n    attach_symbol_names,\n    compute_performance_metrics,\n    compute_trade_statistics,\n    load_benchmark_frame,\n    load_csv,\n    load_json,\n    load_all_trade_rows,\n    parse_float,\n    positions_export_payload,\n    prepare_performance_frame,\n    resolve_path,\n    sanitize_for_json,\n)\nfrom paper_profile_utils import (  # type: ignore\n    profile_name_from_config,\n    profile_slug_from_config,\n    report_path,\n)\n\n\ndef fmt(value: Any, digits: int = 2, suffix: str = \"\") -> str:\n    try:\n        number = float(value)\n    except Exception:\n        return \"-\"\n    if pd.isna(number):\n        return \"-\"\n    return f\"{number:,.{digits}f}{suffix}\"\n\n\ndef resolve_account_file(cfg: dict[str, Any], profile_slug: str) -> Path:\n    default = report_path(REPORT_DIR, \"account_latest\", profile_slug=profile_slug).relative_to(PROJECT_ROOT)\n    return resolve_path(str(cfg.get(\"account_latest_file\", default)))\n\n\ndef resolve_curve_file(cfg: dict[str, Any], profile_slug: str) -> Path:\n    default = report_path(REPORT_DIR, \"nav_curve\", profile_slug=profile_slug).relative_to(PROJECT_ROOT)\n    return resolve_path(str(cfg.get(\"nav_curve_file\", default)))\n\n\ndef resolve_positions_file(cfg: dict[str, Any], profile_slug: str) -> Path:\n    default = report_path(REPORT_DIR, \"positions_latest\", profile_slug=profile_slug).relative_to(PROJECT_ROOT)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":13,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport html\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\n\nfrom generate_dashboard_portal import write_dashboard_portal  # type: ignore\nfrom generate_paper_trading_dashboard import (  # type: ignore\n    as_records,\n    attach_symbol_names,\n    compute_performance_metrics,\n    compute_trade_statistics,\n    load_benchmark_frame,\n    load_csv,\n    load_json,\n    load_all_trade_rows,\n    parse_float,\n    positions_export_payload,\n    prepare_performance_frame,\n    resolve_path,\n    sanitize_for_json,\n)\nfrom paper_profile_utils import (  # type: ignore\n    profile_name_from_config,\n    profile_slug_from_config,\n    report_path,\n)\n\n\ndef fmt(value: Any, digits: int = 2, suffix: str = \"\") -> str:\n    try:\n        number = float(value)\n    except Exception:\n        return \"-\"\n    if pd.isna(number):\n        return \"-\"\n    return f\"{number:,.{digits}f}{suffix}\"\n\n\ndef resolve_account_file(cfg: dict[str, Any], profile_slug: str) -> Path:\n    default = report_path(REPORT_DIR, \"account_latest\", profile_slug=profile_slug).relative_to(PROJECT_ROOT)\n    return resolve_path(str(cfg.get(\"account_latest_file\", default)))\n\n\ndef resolve_curve_file(cfg: dict[str, Any], profile_slug: str) -> Path:\n    default = report_path(REPORT_DIR, \"nav_curve\", profile_slug=profile_slug).relative_to(PROJECT_ROOT)\n    return resolve_path(str(cfg.get(\"nav_curve_file\", default)))\n\n\ndef resolve_positions_file(cfg: dict[str, Any], profile_slug: str) -> Path:\n    default = report_path(REPORT_DIR, \"positions_latest\", profile_slug=profile_slug).relative_to(PROJECT_ROOT)","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775482796786}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e92ce5e","parentId":"a8c62dc3","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:40:09.666Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The paper trading dashboard is generating a large JSON payload. This is sent as a Feishu interactive card. Let me understand the structure.\n\nActually, I think the key optimization for paper trading profiles is:1. Make the dashboard card more concise - currently it shows all 3 profiles in detail, but Zhang Ling only cares about v4_3 now\n2. Add a \"TL;DR\" section at the top\n3. Focus on what's actionable\n\nFor the data source health probe, the main issue is that it sends a card every time there's any price divergence, even when it's just market noise. We could add a threshold so it only sends when divergence is severe.\n\nFor the background cycle, let me look at what it generates.\n\n\nI should focus on the most impactful changes: simplifying the paper trading dashboard to prioritize v4_3 with a concise summary, adding a divergence threshold to the health probe so it only alerts on significant issues, and cleaning up the background cycle report. Since the paper trading profiles cron runs daily and already produces compact Feishu cards, I could make it even more streamlined by highlighting v4_3 and reducing the volume of other profiles. The health probe needs better threshold logic to distinguish between normal market noise and actual problems.","thinkingSignature":"40c7d25fa57a9dcae31fd1eba70d609f8a3dadba2c4d45686e9d2ccd65a717a7"},{"type":"text","text":"让我看一下这几个关键脚本的推送逻辑：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bbedadb37dpd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"feishu_post\\|alert\\|divergence\\|BLOCK\\|GREEN\\|status\\|watch_guarded\\|risk_level\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_investment_research_data_source_health_probe.py 2>/dev/null | grep -v \"def \\|#\" | head -25"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":12