{"type":"message","id":"c546cf1c","parentId":"85db1337","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:42:05.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good understanding of the code. Let me make the optimizations:\n\n1. **Paper trading profiles (`deliver_paper_comparison_to_feishu`)**: \n   - Prioritize v4_3_aggressive in the table\n   - Add a TL;DR line at the top of the card\n   - Reduce holdings to top 3 per profile instead of 5\n   - Add a \"most actionable\" badge\n\n2. **Data source health probe (`deliver_data_source_health_to_feishu`)**:\n   - Only send for BLOCK/ALERT status, skip watch_guarded and normal\n   - Or: Only send if there's an actual alert condition\n\n3. **Background cycle (`run_investment_research_background_cycle`)**:\n   - Already being optimized through the render improvements we made earlier\n\nLet me focus on these three. I'll start with the most impactful - the paper profiles dashboard.","thinkingSignature":"fab22cebf91a58343ea220ffca99f5d5b8297a2662ab0384f8d220fc85dfcde2"},{"type":"text","text":"好，现在动手优化三个最嘈杂的：\n\n**1. 纸盘对比卡片**：精简 holdings，突出 v4_3，加 TL;DR\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_915v976vzkuy_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/paper_profile_utils.py","old_string":"def _build_paper_comparison_elements(configs: list[dict], paper_nav_map: dict, positions_map: dict) -> list[dict]:\n    \"\"\"\n    Build Feishu card element blocks for the paper comparison dashboard.\n    Displays: table header, per-profile rows, and per-profile top holdings.\n    \"\"\"\n    # ---------- table ----------\n    elements: list[dict] = [\n        {\n            \"tag\": \"table\",\n            \"columns\": [\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"left\"},\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n            ],\n            \"elements\": [\n                [\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"**Profile**\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"NAV\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"Total Return\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"Annual Return\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"Sharpe\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"Max DD\"},\n                ]\n            ],\n        }\n    ]\n\n    for cfg in configs:\n        slug = cfg.get(\"profile_slug\", \"\")\n        name = cfg.get(\"profile_name\", slug)\n        key = slug\n        nav = nav_map.get(key, {})\n        positions = positions_map.get(key, [])\n\n        nav_value = nav.get(\"nav\", \"-\")\n        if isinstance(nav_value, float):\n            nav_value = f\"{nav_value:,.0f}\"\n\n        total_return = nav.get(\"total_return_pct\")\n        annual_return = nav.get(\"annual_return_pct\")\n        sharpe = nav.get(\"sharpe\")\n        max_dd = nav.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\")\n        status = cfg.get(\"status\", \"UNKNOWN\")\n        status_color = _status_color(status)\n\n        def f(v: Any) -> str:\n            return str(v) if v is not None else \"-\"\n\n        def pct(v: Any) -> str:\n            if v is None:\n                return \"-\"\n            return f\"{float(v):.2f}%\"\n\n        elements.append(\n            {\n                \"tag\": \"table\",\n                \"columns\": [\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"left\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                ],\n                \"elements\": [\n                    [\n                        {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": f\"**{name}**\"},\n                        {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": f\"**{f(nav_value)}**\"},\n                        {\n                            \"tag\": \"markdown\",\n                            \"content\": f\"{pct(total_return)}\",\n                        },\n                        {\n                            \"tag\": \"markdown\",\n                            \"content\": f\"{pct(annual_return)}\",\n                        },\n                        {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": f\"{f(sharpe)}\"},\n                        {\n                            \"tag\": \"markdown\",\n                            \"content\": f\"<font color='{status_color}'>{pct(max_dd)}</font>\",\n                        },\n                    ]\n                ],\n            }\n        )\n\n        # ---------- holdings ----------\n        if positions:\n            top_holdings = sorted(positions, key=lambda x: x.get(\"weight_pct\", 0), reverse=True)[:5]\n            holding_lines = [f\"**Top {len(top_holdings)} Holdings ({name})**\"]\n            for i, pos in enumerate(top_holdings, 1):\n                code = pos.get(\"ts_code\", pos.get(\"stock_code\", \"?\"))\n                stock_name = pos.get(\"name\", \"?\")\n                weight = pos.get(\"weight_pct\", 0)\n                pnl_pct = pos.get(\"pnl_pct\", 0)\n                pnl_str = f\"<font color='red'>{pnl_pct:.2f}%</font>\" if pnl_pct > 0 else f\"<font color='green'>{pnl_pct:.2f}%</font>\"\n                holding_lines.append(f\"{i}. {stock_name}({code}) {weight:.2f}% {pnl_str}\")\n\n            elements.append({\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"\\n\".join(holding_lines), \"text_align\": \"left\"})\n        else:\n            elements.append(\n                {\n                    \"tag\": \"markdown\",\n                    \"content\": f\"**Top Holdings ({name})**: *No positions*\",\n                    \"text_align\": \"left\",\n                }\n            )\n\n        elements.append({\"tag\": \"hr\"})\n\n    return elements","new_string":"def _build_paper_comparison_elements(configs: list[dict], paper_nav_map: dict, positions_map: dict) -> list[dict]:\n    \"\"\"\n    Build Feishu card element blocks for the paper comparison dashboard.\n    Displays: TL;DR summary, table (v4_3 first), and per-profile top 3 holdings.\n    \"\"\"\n    # ---------- TL;DR summary line ----------\n    tldr_lines = []\n    for cfg in configs:\n        slug = cfg.get(\"profile_slug\", \"\")\n        nav = paper_nav_map.get(slug, {})\n        ann = nav.get(\"annual_return_pct\")\n        total = nav.get(\"total_return_pct\")\n        mdd = nav.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\")\n        status = cfg.get(\"status\", \"UNKNOWN\")\n        name = cfg.get(\"profile_name\", slug)\n        if ann is not None:\n            emoji = \"🟢\" if status == \"ACTIVE\" else \"⚠️\"\n            sign = \"+\" if ann >= 0 else \"\"\n            tldr_lines.append(f\"{emoji}{name}: {sign}{ann:.1f}%\")\n    tldr_content = \" | \".join(tldr_lines) if tldr_lines else \"*No active paper profiles*\"\n\n    elements: list[dict] = [\n        {\n            \"tag\": \"markdown\",\n            \"content\": f\"**📊 模拟盘速览** {tldr_content}\",\n        },\n        {\"tag\": \"hr\"},\n        # ---------- table ----------\n        {\n            \"tag\": \"table\",\n            \"columns\": [\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"left\"},\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n            ],\n            \"elements\": [\n                [\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"**Profile**\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"NAV\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"Total Return\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"Annual Return\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"Sharpe\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"Max DD\"},\n                ]\n            ],\n        },\n    ]\n\n    # Reorder: v4_3_aggressive first\n    def sort_key(cfg):\n        return 0 if cfg.get(\"profile_slug\") == \"v4_3_aggressive\" else 1\n\n    sorted_configs = sorted(configs, key=sort_key)\n\n    for cfg in sorted_configs:\n        slug = cfg.get(\"profile_slug\", \"\")\n        name = cfg.get(\"profile_name\", slug)\n        is_v4_3 = slug == \"v4_3_aggressive\"\n        nav = paper_nav_map.get(slug, {})\n        positions = positions_map.get(slug, [])\n\n        nav_value = nav.get(\"nav\", \"-\")\n        if isinstance(nav_value, float):\n            nav_value = f\"{nav_value:,.0f}\"\n\n        total_return = nav.get(\"total_return_pct\")\n        annual_return = nav.get(\"annual_return_pct\")\n        sharpe = nav.get(\"sharpe\")\n        max_dd = nav.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\")\n        status = cfg.get(\"status\", \"UNKNOWN\")\n        status_color = _status_color(status)\n\n        def f(v: Any) -> str:\n            return str(v) if v is not None else \"-\"\n\n        def pct(v: Any) -> str:\n            if v is None:\n                return \"-\"\n            return f\"{float(v):.2f}%\"\n\n        # Bold v4_3 row label\n        label = f\"**{'⭐' if is_v4_3 else ''}{name}**\"\n        elements.append(\n            {\n                \"tag\": \"table\",\n                \"columns\": [\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"left\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                    {\"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": 96, \"horizontal_align\": \"right\"},\n                ],\n                \"elements\": [\n                    [\n                        {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": label},\n                        {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": f\"**{f(nav_value)}**\"},\n                        {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": pct(total_return)},\n                        {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": pct(annual_return)},\n                        {\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": f\"{f(sharpe)}\"},\n                        {\n                            \"tag\": \"markdown\",\n                            \"content\": f\"<font color='{status_color}'>{pct(max_dd)}</font>\",\n                        },\n                    ]\n                ],\n            }\n        )\n\n        # ---------- top 3 holdings (v4_3 only in detail, others minimal) ----------\n        if positions:\n            top_holdings = sorted(positions, key=lambda x: x.get(\"weight_pct\", 0), reverse=True)\n            if is_v4_3:\n                show = top_holdings[:3]\n                holding_lines = [f\"**⭐ 持仓（{name}前3）**\"]\n                for i, pos in enumerate(show, 1):\n                    code = pos.get(\"ts_code\", pos.get(\"stock_code\", \"?\"))\n                    stock_name = pos.get(\"name\", \"?\")\n                    weight = pos.get(\"weight_pct\", 0)\n                    pnl_pct = pos.get(\"pnl_pct\", 0)\n                    pnl_str = f\"+{pnl_pct:.1f}%\" if pnl_pct >= 0 else f\"{pnl_pct:.1f}%\"\n                    color = \"red\" if pnl_pct > 0 else \"green\"\n                    holding_lines.append(f\"{i}. {stock_name}({code}) {weight:.1f}% {pnl_str}\")\n                if len(top_holdings) > 3:\n                    holding_lines.append(f\"...等共{len(top_holdings)}只\")\n                elements.append({\"tag\": \"markdown\", \"content\": \"\\n\".join(holding_lines), \"text_align\": \"left\"})\n            else:\n                # Non-v4_3: just show top 1\n                top = top_holdings[0]\n                code = top.get(\"ts_code\", top.get(\"stock_code\", \"?\"))\n                stock_name = top.get(\"name\", \"?\")\n                weight = top.get(\"weight_pct\", 0)\n                elements.append(\n                    {\n                        \"tag\": \"markdown\",\n                        \"content\": f\"持仓: *{stock_name}({code}) {weight:.1f}%*\",\n                        \"text_align\": \"left\",\n                    }\n                )\n        else:\n            elements.append(\n                {\n                    \"tag\": \"markdown\",\n                    \"content\": f\"持仓: *空仓*\",\n                    \"text_align\": \"left\",\n                }\n            )\n\n        elements.append({\"tag\": \"hr\"})\n\n    return elements"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":130887,"output":2997,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":155351,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775482864287,"responseId":"0622eaf0915927e750825fdf6786f6e9"}}
