{"type":"message","id":"d944c827","parentId":"9df9bf1a","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:57:50.065Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done. Let me summarize what was fixed.","thinkingSignature":"98de5afc74cfbf5801b9e711b52a2123f2be1c0f833a6bc8e45571109d086b47"},{"type":"text","text":"全部搞定。来个总结：\n\n---\n\n**本次优化了 6 个 Feishu 推送脚本：**\n\n| 脚本 | 修复内容 |\n|------|---------|\n| `check_stop_loss.py` | `is_trading_day()` 升级为腾讯行情 API（含节假日） |\n| `generate_daily_exec_card.py` | `is_trading_day()` 升级 + 持仓最多显示5只（原来不限） |\n| `generate_actionable_brief.py` | `is_trading_day()` 升级为腾讯行情 API |\n| `generate_daily_position_report.py` | `is_trading_day()` 升级 + 持仓日报只显示前5只 |\n| `push_breadth_strict_oos_paper_to_feishu.py` | 新增腾讯行情 API 非交易日校验 |\n| `push_paper_trade_fill_to_feishu.py` | 新增腾讯行情 API 非交易日校验 |\n\n**核心改进：**\n- 之前：只用 `weekday < 5` 判断，假期最后一天可能乱跑\n- 现在：腾讯行情 API 第30字段返回真实日期，严格卡死非交易日\n\n明天 4/7 节后第一天，各 cron 会正常触发，但推送量会干净很多 📉"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42293,"output":271,"cacheRead":21467,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64031,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775483861705,"responseId":"0622eed6e4523fe6ba197fe175a8dd46"}}
