{"type":"message","id":"79bfcf34","parentId":"bda04218","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:58:08.866Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ou6izogjvsqd_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 建议：所有A股节假日判断统一用腾讯行情API，不要依赖qlib calendar\n\n### aggregate_intelligence_brief.py 注意事项\n- 全球宏观研报卡片由此脚本生成（image看到的是2026-04-03版本）\n- 数据源：DeepLX(Tariff news) + Tavily(News) + Firecrawl(Web) + Tavily Search\n\n[3 more lines in file. Use offset=125 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775483888864}}
{"type":"message","id":"b54de581","parentId":"79bfcf34","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:58:22.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the file ends at line 127. Let me append the new content about the 21:57 session.","thinkingSignature":"63ee651881164b632c2e11c89c3ee8462997543fbc854e000ebb5af93d2c0fc5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vxwyz1oa7661_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-coding-agent/memory/2026-04-06.md","content":"\n\n## 晚间补充（21:57）— 定时任务推送优化\n\n### 问题\n大部分脚本只用 `weekday < 5` 判断交易日，**没有排除 A 股节假日**（清明/五一/十一等），导致假期最后一天可能乱触发。\n\n### 修复了 6 个 Feishu 推送脚本\n\n| 脚本 | 修复内容 |\n|------|---------|\n| `check_stop_loss.py` | `is_trading_day()` 升级为腾讯行情 API（含节假日） |\n| `generate_daily_exec_card.py` | 升级交易日判断 + 持仓最多显示5只（原来不限，太多） |\n| `generate_actionable_brief.py` | 升级为腾讯行情 API 交易日判断 |\n| `generate_daily_position_report.py` | 升级交易日判断 + 持仓日报只显示前5只 |\n| `push_breadth_strict_oos_paper_to_feishu.py` | 新增腾讯行情 API 非交易日校验 |\n| `push_paper_trade_fill_to_feishu.py` | 新增腾讯行情 API 非交易日校验 |\n\n### 腾讯行情 API 判断逻辑（通用）\n```python\ndef is_trading_day() -> bool:\n    try:\n        req = urllib.request.Request(\n            \"http://qt.gtimg.cn/q=sh000001\",\n            headers={\"User-Agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0\"}\n        )\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=5) as resp:\n            content = resp.read().decode(\"gbk\", errors=\"replace\")\n        for line in content.split(\";\"):\n            if \"sh000001\" in line:\n                parts = line.split(\"~\")\n                if len(parts) > 30:\n                    mkt_str = parts[30].strip()[:8]\n                    market_date = f\"{mkt_str[:4]}-{mkt_str[4:6]}-{mkt_str[6:8]}\"\n                    today = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n                    return market_date == today\n                break\n        return datetime.now().weekday() < 5\n    except Exception:\n        return datetime.now().weekday() < 5\n```\n\n### 飞书推送 target ID 确认（再次确认）\n- 私聊: `user:ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae`\n- 来福投研会群: `user:ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080`\n\n### 已提交\n- quant_projects: `a6173ebc8` — 全面优化盘前报告（CB市场+v4.3参数+清晰信号）\n- workspace-coding-agent: `bf0e5ab` — 更新HEARTBEAT.md和今日memory\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":10284,"output":671,"cacheRead":11449,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22404,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775483888867,"responseId":"0622eef1305249974876e181490cbf9d"}}
