{"type":"message","id":"57de6484","parentId":"8f58f23c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T15:14:23.020Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b520892196ca0c33ad0cecec971e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-06 23:14 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b520892196ca0c33ad0cecec971e]\n张玲: ## Session Health Awareness\nLong sessions slow down and risk timeout-blackout. You are responsible for keeping your session healthy.\n### At Startup\n1. Check your session file: `wc -l ~/.openclaw/agents/coding-agent/sessions/*.jsonl | sort -n`\n   - If any session file > 500 lines → session is **too heavy**\n   - If > 1000 lines → session is **critical** — write `memory/context.md` now and tell the user at the start of your reply: \"我的会话历史已经很长，可能会变慢。建议开一个新的 coding agent session 来继续任务，我会把当前进度写到 memory 文件里。\"\n### During Long Tasks\n- If a command will take > 2 minutes, say upfront: \"正在执行 X（大任务），预计需要 N 分钟，完成后立刻汇报。\"\n- Never go silent for > 3 minutes during a task. If stuck, say what you're waiting on.\n### After Completing a Task\nBefore you finish any substantial task:\n1. Write a **3-line summary** to `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` under `## Coding Agent 进度`\n2. Update `memory/context.md` with current state, next step, and any pending items\n3. If the session file is now > 300 lines, say: \"这个任务完成了。我建议开新 session 继续下一个任务，防止上下文过长导致超时。\"\n### Never Appear Dead\nIf context is > 75% (long session + deep task), proactively say:\n\"当前上下文较长，我会尽量快速完成。如果我停了很久，请发 '继续' 打破等待。\""}],"timestamp":1775488463017}}
